I was in a building with the actor, Jake Johnson. There were huge rooms made of glass bricks in the centre of the building. They were empty but I knew they were for whales. Jake and I were wandering through the building, I think making sure it was ready for something? At that point, a flood of water could be seen coming from the upper floor. We were at the opposite side of a swimming pool and Jake thought we would be safe but once the water hit, it overflowed the already full swimming pool and we were washed away. We ended up confined to a corner in each other's arms. I thought he was going to kiss me but there was a weird noise and a bubble seemed to be filling the room. We were safe in the corner but the bubble exploded and covered everything in sticky residue, like the adhesive on cards affixed to paper. We left the area, pulling the adhesive off our skin and looking for help.

I was in a pub with some old friends from high school. Other high school friends were there but I was deliberately ignoring them. I was queuing for a drink at the bar whilst chatting to Richard. I can't remember what we were talking about but I remember resting my head on his arm because it was taking so long to get served. After this, I was talking to the actor Jake Johnson about my night out. He had been away for the weekend so we were telling each other what we had done. He got upset that I had been out with other men and I was trying to explain to him what a big deal it was that I wasn't panicking about him being gone. I told him it meant I trusted him and loved him but he maintained he was upset at my behaviour. I ran upstairs and cried on my bed.

I was planning a birthday party for my son when I had a panicked visit from Rachel who thought her daughter Freya had mumps. We then got into a weird argument about what mumps actually were and I was trying to explain that Freya had been vaccinated so couldn't have mumps. It was very tense and Rachel was very upset. I was trying to prepare the party food and was struggling to comfort her, diagnose Freya and get ready for the party.
I had returned to my parents home after being away with family. My Dad asked if they'd been starving me as I'd lost so much weight. I said I was hungry.

I had argued quite severely with a man who was threatening me and hurt his arm. I had pacified him by saying I would buy him a drink. I found a raspberry sour beer via a brewery that caused psychological distress and hallucinations and bought one for him. I also got one for myself and I couldn't work out why.

I was backstage getting staff ready for the show and Andrew was also working there, or maybe he was just there for me. I was being distant and messaging on my phone a lot. We had sleeping bunks at the back of the theatre. I was talking to one of the techs, he was new and we were flirting. We kept getting closer to kissing and we finally did. He and I were in my bunk and Andrew was somewhere else. I wasnt sure if it was a dream or not and I ended up having sex with the tech. it ended abruptly and I woke up I checked my phone and had a message from the tech saying "last night was better than sex". Which confused me as I was sure we'd had sex but the message wasn't clear if we had or hadn't. I was scrolling up the message history and we had been texting back and forth, as no was Andrew came around the corner and asked me where I'd been. I told him I'd just been on my phone and he nodded but looked sad, like he knew the truth.

I was sharing a bed with my mum and my aunty. We lived with an old woman behind a gas station, aunty was a social worker but saved people. Like a super hero. She was saying you always had to run or you wouldn't get there in time. She told me one time she saw someone get hit by a car and she didn't do anything and she told the police it was because she was running for one of her cases but they questioned her and found out she lied.  I was following her. As she ran to a child that was in danger.  Then all of a sudden I was in Charlie's Angels, and I knew I was one of them but didn't know which one. I could see myself as each character as if watching myself from above. I realised I was Drew Barrymore. We were running to save three young boys. I was carrying to of them , running from a street explosion to our car about 50 metres away that I knew was fireproof. Made it to the car that was fireproof. Everyone was cheering us, Marilyn Monroe was at the end of the street and I flashed her my breasts in a way of jubilation and she flashed me back.

I felt uncomfortable, like I was doing something wrong. I was sitting at the computer, my boss was standing behind me and I was logging in to my work computer. It started syncing with my phone, I realised that it was because I had chosen to set my work computer to my Google account and all of my photos were on there. I looked over at my colleagues computer, she had just called my name, and my nude photographs I had taken for my partner were one by one loading onto her screen. I tried to grab my phone and disconnect it from the system. I somehow knew that they were loading onto everyone's computer at work. I wasn't able to.

I had put cakey makeup on my face, just foundation, and even though it was imperfect I knew I was the only one who knew and everyone was staring at me. I felt attractive and desired. I was at a function, and one of the directors from work was there and he instantly came over to me and slid his arm around my waist and led me off into a bedroom. We had sex and it felt very fun and naughty, but I felt incredibly self-assured and confident and didn't at all feel guilty. We lay in bed laughing and talking, I don't remember what we said but it felt incredibly comfortable and nice.

I didn't have a sense of smell and so I was worried I had covid. I was driving on a long straight road in the city that was never-ending, it had a traffic light every ten metres and every time I would just miss the green light and wait and go and just miss it again.
I was invited to friend F house. Didn't want to go because of coronavirus.

Travelled to Machu Picchu. There were a lot of tourists walking along the road to hike up the mountain. Was talking to girls along the way about hiking gear. They were in shorts and short dresses, and were very sunburnt. We joked about how obvious it was that we weren't hikers. I told them I learnt to wear longer layers when I moved there a few months earlier, because the sun is very strong in high altitudes. They thought it would be hot in Peru so hadn't brought proper layers, and were now feeling cold.  Faded to a different scene in same dream. Was shopping in a town nearby and looking for jeans. They had TK Maxx tags on the jeans. Tried on a pair of Hobbs jeans, but was too big even though it was my size. Looked at some tops to try on. Was with my best friend M and possibly other friends but can't remember who.

Was housesitting a flat for a couple of friends ( J & R ) while they were away. Flat was a bit dark and there was a massive rug on the floor. My parents were there and because I was chatting to them I forgot the keys and the doors shut behind me. My parents got in their car to drive away (they were in separate cars), I waved down my dad who had a spare key that J had given him in case this happened.  I took the key, got the keys from the flat and returned the spare to Dad. It was raining while we were standing in the courtyard. Mum told me I should spend more time outside in the courtyard. I thought the people who lived in the building (several flats) would have enjoyed using it during lockdown. Although it was small, so I wondered how they arranged to take turns so they weren't too close to each other.

completing this dream report 2 week period. Had to put my email address in. I wasn't very happy about that because I thought it couldn't be anonymous then. Put it in because I wanted to be kept informed about the study. There was also a competition if I entered my email.

Was going to meet up with a friend at the park. She postponed because a friend's mum died and she had to help her friend. I went out with parents instead. It was sunny and warm, 27 degrees when I checked my phone. Was thinking about a holiday. It would be nice to go away before it gets cold and dark. I imagined Spain in the dream and the beach there. Switched to being on a water slide/bicycle obstacle course in Denmark on the border where there is a bridge to Sweden. It was fun. I don't know if I knew anyone with me, but I made friends with another girl who was doing the course as well. We found a secret door through a fake washing machine with more levels so we could extend the obstacle course. Switched to chatting in a group with a friend about a guy we all thought she liked. She was embarrassed and then realised she did in fact like N.

Was by a river on holiday with friends. River was familiar from another real life holiday in Wales, although in the dream I think I was in South America. All my friends were swimming in the river and told me to jump in, but it was very murky and the edges were full of floating giant snails. Harmless, but I couldn't figure out how to get in the river without jumping into a sea of snails. There was a baby whale. Orange, with huge lips, cartoonlike. A nondescript male friend was patting it and it was eating lots of snails. I was nervous of it because of it's size, and wondered where the mother was, but also wanted to go in the water. I can't remember if I ended up going in or not, I think I was happy to watch. Switched to being on a beach. Two friends, one S, one nondescript, were running. They were being obnoxious and we had an argument. Switched to being in a hospital. I was an old man for some reason, and feeling helpless. I called out to the nurse that I needed to use the toilet, so I got out of bed to urinate. We were speaking in Spanish, and I felt alone and out of place. I don't think I was sick, just old.

Was on plane journey to Ukraine for some reason. Family were on plane too. I was getting frustrated that my mum refused to wear her mask properly. She didn't think it was a big deal. I was trying to get them to wear N95 masks, but she said she couldn't breathe properly in it and wanted to be left alone. I thought the agreement between us to travel was that we would all be extra cautious and do what it took to travel safely. Was looking at toilet door on plane. For some reason someone had died in the toilet. Didn't see it, but there was a sign or something. Because there were 4 of us, I worried that one was left on another aisle with other people.

Dreamt that friend was pregnant. She was kind of upset about it as unexpected. Was on public transport trying to get somewhere with older brother. People weren't wearing masks. I was getting frustrated and didn't feel safe. Don't know why I was on public transport or where I was going. Lost brother as one of us missed train while the other was on. Waited for a bit until brother arrived at my station. Had been observing people, no one cared about social distancing.
Laptop screen edging completely broke off. Was surprised that laptop was still working. People were trying to take a look at it, but I told them to stay away in case it broke more.
There were 2 people with Russian accents talking to me or near me.

I was at a high school checking out the facilities for my grandsons to attend. Walked through the halls & rooms with the group listening to the principal & other teachers explain everything. I needed to go to the toilet so left the group to find one. I came across 3 guys huddled together & got the vibe that I shouldn't let them see me so hid nearby. I could just hear snippets of what they were talking about but it definitely sounded like they were planning something illegal. Next thing I recall is I was at one of my daughter's friend's house. She asked why I was in the area & I told her about looking at the high school etc. She got all excited & told me that's the one she had gone to & she still had access. Suddenly we were jogging along a path in the bush taking the short cut to school. She told me there had always been something dodgy going on at the school. Just before we got there, police started blowing whistles & yelling at us to stop. She told me to go down another path as she took off in the opposite direction. As I ran I saw the same 3 guys lurking in the shadows. I turned around & waited for the cops to get closer then called out to them about the 3 guys. They tried to run but the police got them. They had bags of headlights & other bits of bikes with them. The police told me they had been trying to catch the group for years. I realised I still had to go to the toilet.

We were getting ready for a party in the front garden at my Mum's house. Suddenly I was cooking lots of bacon & eggs. There was a huge pile of it on a table but I kept cooking. The eggs looked like shelled boiled eggs but I had been frying them. No one arrived & everyone that had been helping get ready were murmuring amongst themselves until some yelled out "Change of venue". There was a whole lot of scurrying about & suddenly everything has been packed into cars. I was still cooking but this time it was some sort of greenish vegetable & poached eggs. I laid them on a platter & broke the eggs in a nice presentation then poured hot water on it all to keep warm. I was trying to arrange for the platters to be put in a car when my Dad told me to leave them. "They'll come for that after we've gone", he said. There was some discussion was had about coffee. I looked at the coffee machine & it had heaps of pipes & tubes coming from a big coffee bean funnel which was sitting in the branches of a nearby tree. There seemed to be an argument going on behind me & my Dad/uncle said "I've fixed it, look". We all turned to where he pointed. All the tubing had been taped up & converged into one small pipe. The pipe has above a saucepan & the coffee was dripping slowly into it. Everyone seemed happy with that. Someone put their hand in the large bowl off eggs & leeks and stirred them around. "Looks good, yowch still hot too" they said . I looked in the bowl & wondered what happened to the platter as well as marveling that the eggs still looked the same as when I cut them up, running yolks etc even though they were in hot water & someone had just swirled them around. The water was clear but should have been cloudy. My stomach lurched at the thought of eating them. I looked around at the people to figure out who was in there.

I was working in a donut/cake/pastry shop. It was one of those that are in the middle of a shopping centre, like an island. There were 3 other staff plus the manager    but no customers. I took a phone call & a female voice asked to order a 'slab of donut scrolley things'. I wasn't sure what she meant as I hadn't worked there long so asked the older woman of the staff. She pointed to a half tray of some mushy stuff drizzled with icing. I noticed that there wasn't many other items in the cases. I went back to the phone & told them we had some. The caller asked for them to be put aside & they'd pick them up at 7:30. I presumed pm as it was after lunch already. She told me the name was Daniel Dans. That confused me at first but I asked her to clarify & repeated the name out loud. The manager heard & told me to give her the phone. She was gushing all over the place then got angry with me after she hung up the phone. She had thought it was someone important but had misheard the name. I couldn't work out what the important name would have been so just shrugged it off.  Then I was in a car with 5 people as an observer & it was the Dans family. Danielle (not Daniel!) was telling her parents that she had placed the order but wouldn't 7:30 be cutting it fine. Her Dad replied 'No, we can't pick up the puppies until 9:30. No one is stopping me getting them today, we've waited weeks for them.'

I was watching four people at railings near bus stop. Thought they were waiting for a bus. They all suddenly started to do different exercises on the railings & bus stop pole. They didn't have 'exercise' clothes on so it was unexpected. I was suddenly watching them from an upstairs apartment & noticed one of them had left. Two guys came up to them & did something (couldn't see).  Two of the original three started to put on helmets (old leather flying type of helmet) presumably to ride the motorbikes that were parked on the footpath. The bikes morphed into scooters & the woman took off her helmet & threw it at hers. The third guy climbed onto the railings again & stood on the top balancing with his arms out. The door to my apartment crashed open & 2 guys came inside. One of them appeared to live there as he was opening drawers saying "I know I have one here". They were arguing about what they had done downstairs. The other guy said "We have to finish it or our lives won't be worth anything. I already told him we got her". I wasn't scared as I presumed they were talking about the woman downstairs. The first guy said  "I've got a bigger battery here, I know it. We just have to give her an overdose of charge, that'll stop her". I looked out the window again & the two with helmets were sitting against the railing, twitching with blue sparks coming out of the helmets.  The guy on the railing was squatting on top of the bus stop pole.

I was in a maze. I ended up on the otherside at an opening. There were a bunch of people grouped around me & I was stressed to the max. My heart was pounding & my hands/face sweating. There was something flying past the opening which I couldn't work out at first. It looked like a lift without doors but then it was more like a guillotine. It seemed to be both. A sideways lift I had to jump into to take me away from the maze plus a guillotine going up & down really quickly. The lift moved to the right & left also so you had to time the jump perfectly. I think some people in front of me tried it & only one got through. The others were cut down with blood & guts were everywhere. It was suddenly my turn. Not because I was ready to try but only because the group were pushing towards it & I somehow ended up at the front. The blood etc was gone as if to give false sense of it being ok. I tried to work out the timing of the lift being there without the blade & nearly had it. Every time the lift came in from the right the blade was a bit slower. I just needed a few more passes then I could confirm it. The lift came from the left & suddenly the group pushed forward & I stumbled toward the lift as the blade was coming down.

I drove my ^family to a cemetery & let them out near a mausoleum. My father told me to "park the bentleigh next to the gate away from the underclass. I drove to the parking near the gate but it was full. Some people had pushed some rocks aside & parked on grassy garden area. I went to park in the last space but noticed a lincoln continental appeared to have been pushed further onto the grass down a light embankment. There were black paint scratches on the side so I presumed it had been moved with a car. I didn't want to park our car there as it was black too & they might think I'd done it. Plus it would block the other car in. I drove a little further and saw another spot where rocks had been moved for parking but this place had a 'No Parking - fines will be issued' sign. I park amongst the rocks as I did a mental calculation of the odds of being fined & how much. I got out & ran towards the mausoleum. When we returned to the car a couple of council parking officers were sitting in a quad bike with a yellow flashing light on the roof blocking our car. The passenger got out & spoke to my father. I could hear only snippets of the conversation but it sounded like he was giving us a warning this time but no fine. My father wouldn't let it go as if he was insulted. He seemed to rant at the guy for quite awhile until the driver of the quad bike said "come on, this jobs not worth it" & started to drive off.  Suddenly I was sitting on a tandem pushbike at a kiosk waiting for my father. He brought a huge bag of food out & plonked it in the basket at the front of the bike. He walked away. The bike started to tip over so the guy in the kiosk rushed out & helped me hold the bike up. We waited for my father for ages.  Then I was sitting on a multi person bike. It had single seats at the front & back plus 4 rows of double seats. The double seats were like the ones in trains or buses. Same color material too. My partner was sitting beside me on the 2nd row double seat & there was another bike the same next to us. No one else was around. I think we thought it would be a fun thing to do but it felt sinister the longer we sat there waiting.

We were in the city walking about. Had our little dog with us but he wasn't on a lead so I kept picking him up. I was nervous as could get fined for not being on a lead plus we didn't have any poo bags for him either. Suddenly we were in a big park and there were lots of people around. Next thing we were standing next to a large open carpark. There were cars everywhere with caravans or campers attached. People were heading off on trips. A woman asked us 'why aren't you going too?' I replied 'We can't get a permit'.

Physical words in the way. If you broke them it reduced your energy. Animals just crashed through them so you had to be careful not to let them out. Labrador was in my path. Lady I had worked with was telling me to give it a hug & it will stay, (ie not run & break the words). I was trying to get home. There were Police & a surgeon involved too. I had to break as few words as possible to allow the most senior cop or surgeon to help me. I got a one of them out but don't recall how they helped me.

I was walking down a road & saw a good friend I used to work with. I stopped to talk but she said she was running late for a team meeting. I offered her a lift but she said she couldn't. Then I was walking in a corridor past large rooms with lots of windows discussing something with the  General Manager of the same workplace as my friend. We went into one of the rooms where the team meeting was being held & the Manager running it glared at me. I was confused as to why but went to look for a table to sit at anyway. The others were sitting one to a table so I could only find a little table in the back corner that no one was using. I tried to pull it closer to the group but the others glared at me too. I realised they thought I'd betrayed them in some way by bringing the General Manager. Us arriving together was a coincidence which they realised when he started talking about something unrelated to their meeting.  I then appeared to be in a different place. It was more like an office with cubicles. I was taking some folders off a shelf to take them home for my studies. A woman took them from me saying 'He needs them more than you'. I saw a guy younger than me that was surrounded by work mates cheering him on. When I asked her why she replied 'He's nearly finished his degree'. I said, so was I & asked if we could make a copy & share them. She told me, 'Definitely not!'. I got really angry & was about to walk away so I wouldn't say anything I'd regret when I noticed the work mates giving me a thumbs up & smiling. They were talking about the younger guy behind his back. One of the things I heard was 'At least he's stopped wearing that bright jumpsuit!' I had an image flash through my mind of him in a bright shiny fluoro blue & yellow jumpsuit doing a pose.

Was at work to drive truck with goods to delivery point. I didn't have paperwork. Girl in office wrote the address on my helmet & said it wasn't far. I tried to read the mud map she gave me but couldn't understand it. I went to the other office to get a Melways to find the place myself. I took off my helmet to read the address but couldn't understand the writing. I went back to my truck but couldn't get out of depot as someone had parked a crappy old truck behind me, blocking me in. I was really stressed & concerned I'd be sacked.

Was lying in bed & my partner had restless legs & kept semi kicking. I pushed back his legs trying to get some space as didn't want our little dog to be accidentally kicked off the bed & get hurt. I looked out window then looked down beside bed to see how far the fall would be for our dog. There was no wall and the bed was right next to the edge of the building. Bedroom has changed from being in our house to the penthouse of multi-storey apartments. I had somehow bought a drone & was working out how to fly it. Was hovering over parkland down below when it crashed into a tree. It fell down the tree breaking the camera. When I checked the footage there was only 1 photo (not a video as I expected). I  framed it & put on display in my lounge (original house not penthouse apartment) and called it 'My most expensive picture'.

I was at Mum's house, early morning  & wanted to sit outside on the patio to watch the sunrise. I nearly went outside but I was naked so I went to my bedroom & got a silk nightie to put on. It was hard to get on as I had to put it over the tshirt nightie I was suddenly wearing. As I opened the door to go onto the patio, wearing both nighties, my youngest grandson came into the room with a friends. My Mum & a few other people followed them into the room.  It seemed really crowded but there were only a few people. I didn't go onto the patio. Something happened & there was a sudden need to get my grandson to school. I helped him find his school uniform & left him to change into it while I watched Mum try to make something for his lunch. Something was wrong with food or there wasn't any so my sister went to the shops to buy some. She took forever & my grandson was getting stressed that he'd be late for school. My Mum reassured him it would be ok & reminded him that it was a long walk but my sister wouldn't be much longer.  I raised my arms in exasperation & yelled, "Why didn't she drive like she always does?"  Then we were all back in the family room, which was off the patio, as if none of that had happened. My grandson's friend came through the door crying followed by his Dad. I hadn't met them before and as I went to introduce myself his Dad said they were Chinese/Malaysian & upset with my grandson. Everyone immediately presumed it was a racist issue seeing as he had pointed out  their heritage. I squatted down near the boy & asked him what was wrong. He said he hated my Grandson. Before I could ask another question the other people in the room shouted their own questions. 'Did he call you a name?' 'Was it about your name, skin color, hair?' The boy replied 'No, he didn't say anything mean to me'. 'Did he push you, hit you, take your stuff?', they asked. 'No', he replied again. 'Well why do you hate him', I asked. He's taller than me', was his response. We all had a chuckle & big sigh of relief.  Then I told the little boy about my friend who is 6'4" . He had a friend the same age & height in primary school but over the years his friend grew taller faster than him  & got upset too. When they went to high school my friend had a sudden growth spurt & caught up with his mate. He eventually ended up taller than his mate but they don't care about that anymore.

my friend from high school tied up with invisible thread. Everytime I cut one another seemed to tie her elsewhere. I had to go quickly but carefully using an unpicker. Eventually I got it all off. Then the guy who did it turned up & we wrapped him up in it including over his face. We kept tightening it until it was cutting into parts of him. He started to cry & say he was sorry. A group of people arrived telling us off. One of the girls I think we may have known. Another girl had a baby that was crying but she didn't seem to know what to do. She placed it on the floor & put talcum powder all over it. I told her that wasn't a good idea if it was crying as it might choke. She told me to mind my own business. No one else would step in so I picked up the baby & cleared the powder from its face. I gave it a cuddle & rocked it gently for a few minutes & it stopped crying. The girl smiled at me, said thank you then took the baby & put it back on the floor.
I'm at a shopping centre food court and it's full. No social distancing.

I'm at a pharmacy with my hijabi wearing friend and my trans friend, and we have to get medication for our trans friend but we have to speak in code to the shop assistants who understand what we're looking for. Later, Dan is oblivious to the whole thing.
The word 'conVid...' something

Dream I'm on my way out of a festival and need to use the loo. I find a single small old loo on the side of a building but when I go in there, outside there are heaps of people.  My mum has obtained a calf somehow and wants to give it some sunshine so she lets it out of the garage to roam on our property. But it goes to the abattoir itself. A forewoman assures me she will try and save the calf but i'm not too convinced she can.  I hang up a bath pillow on an inside door towards the back of the house.  Catherine Kelleher passes me on the way to school. Then I think I have to be in school too, but someone tells me no, Kim Wilson got time off for doing a script, so I have today off too. I have two assignments due. And I've barely started so I'm anxious. I get to the kitchen table and Ariana Grande is there as well as a African American rapper but they are also students.

I'm trying to do some corporate espionage and take a lift to the top floor of a posh office building but the lift gets stuck. We need to get rescued and it's quite dangerous. They ask why we needed to get to the top floor and we say we like pressing buttons. As I'm holding onto the lift, it warps, and could fall down the long elevator shaft.  I'm on a video call with Dayne, a talent agent. She closes the call by showing me a funny musical variety show closing sequence. I clap and smile to show my appreciation. I'm in a house but the floor is set out like a word document. I change the alignment to 'justified' but it creates weird formatting spaces. My daughter is apoplectic like I ruined it. I try to fix it and more people come to try and fix it. My mum calls my mobile and I take a wall clock to the kitchen.

I have an acting role, a minor one in a historical drama. We're filming but all the dialogue and actions are in a novel, it's prose, and hard to follow. I miss my cue and fluff a line and realise it's so hard because there's no actual script.  I'm on the top level of a big corporate building. One of my male friends open up the window which is connected to the floor, takes a run up, and pretends to skid out out the window. As we approach the window, we realise instead of a steep drop there's a park beyond the window. We slip out and walk through the grounds which include a tennis court. We walk through then use escalators to get back to our room.  I see a face of a female baby and I know I can't abort her.  I have to let bar staff know that my pregnant friend broke her waters. I take her to the place and there's liquid on the table and cups knocked over.  I go to a small narrow room with a lot of people arranged in a circle, wanting to hear news of the baby, and my friend Julia is drinking tea with a teabag with leather strips in it to give it the taste of leather.

I'm at my workmate Catherine's place and she is looking after 3 small nieces and nephews. To amuse them, she makes a long pretend fart sound. She has a nice apartment. I tell her I need to make sure she's on the invite list for this industry event.  I'm at this industry event and confronted by this guy from primary school PH, who I haven't seen since then who declares his love for me. He shows me all the credit cards he's stolen from me and cut up. His love is really creepy and possessive. All my papers and Dan's papers are everywhere and I'm trying to clean up. Plus a young Asian female guard questions whether I should be at the event.  I'm in a swish hotel with PH but realise I need to leave. I fly down sets of stairs, hide myself in a dark alcove and turn off my phone.  I turn off the electric fire at my parents house with a remote. I then realise I need to go home.  I'm selected to buy new jeans, by these guys who are jeans designers. It's part of a promo video, and all of us there are from a service like Airtasker. I tell them I usually wear black jeans. I try on some blue jeans which are laced with light blue ribbon like ballet shoe laces  Dan and I are catching a bus, we're late. Rena is already on board. We get on and we ask to go to Marrickville but the young female driver says it doesn't go there. It goes to Paddington and other suburbs. We're confused, say our friend is on board but apparently Rena is now going south to Hurstville etc. We figure we'll get to Paddington and find a way home. We pay the fare and get 10c change and join Rena and Rena leaves 10c as a tip for the driver.

There is a cute beagle puppy that someone gave me and it's running up and down stairs.  I need to get something from our neighbours in our apartment block. I knock on their door and I go inside. There are two women. One is wearing a yellow and black designed shirt while cooking. They show me a table with some clothes - there's a collection of shorts. One I pick up is a denim pair of shorts with a really small waist. They want me to try on some of the shorts. There are also towels there. I'm in parents kitchen. Someone, I think my dad, has left leftover food out and not fridged it so I'm annoyed. I chuck some rice in the bin and fridge everything else. For some reason Kylie and her family are in my parents backyard which they've accessed through a trail at the back. They leave.  I'm suddenly then watching a scene from a movie  A man throws leftover chicken and corn soup over a car and an argument starts with the man inside the car. It's a ploy to distract the man from going inside one of the shops. Then the director, a white guy, pauses the scene. An alternate scene runs which is slightly different, still involves the soup throwing. I offer some notes to the director.  We watch an elaborate film for staff that Bazmark made specifically for their employees when going through a shooting hiatus. Someone asks me to guess the film and I guess correctly that it's The Great Gatsby. I see casual photos of myself from various film/TV shoots. I point out one has my boss Jason's foot. I peel back a layer of semi opaque film over an attractive photo of my face labelled with the film's name Younger, but that's not my face. I'm a different person. I'm teenage boy at a school boarding house. It's dark, old, grand manor with dogs. One of the other boys has to travel somewhere so I have to stay the night at the school, as someone has to. Usually I would go home for the night. I'm worried about my contact lenses and my vision being blurry the next day, but understand the boy needs to go.

The first one is of my parents watching a foreign movie on my bed. They had draped my blue and white doona on the bed.  One was Robyn Malcolm on my bed talking to me about something.  One was me and Dan flirting on bed, but he had red dots near his crotch.  One was me going into the bathroom and one of the bathroom lights being broken, flickering weakly and I wanted to tell someone. A fan suddenly bent one of the fan paddles down which told me it was a dream.  One was people, mostly men, laughing outside my balcony.  One was me seeing a shelf in the bathroom, as you walk in, with two big binders on it.  One I was on my bed, looking at a red case which I knew carried CDs or DVDs and I marvelled at how realistic it looked in my dream.

I'm in this gang where we distract while others in the gang rob the place. We're in a shopping mall.  Then the situation inverts and I'm one of the bystanders. We see someone run off but then one of the bad guys runs after him. We can hear the cadence of his prosthetic leg as he runs away. But the guy catches up to him and shoots him.  Then we're in a big field. I'm in a sky blue shiny modern car. We're still being held hostage, and I'm with a blonde girl. Some friends arrive and we convince her to swap seats so our guy friend is in the driver's seat. She does so and he floors it, trying to escape. We drive out of the field, but then we get stuck in a series of smaller and smaller interior maze-like, stairs-like spaces until we can't go further. Then I'm in this magical dreamlike space. The light is soft and warm. There's a payphone. It's a safe place. There's a sense that something wondrous could occur, like a TARDIS landing.

I'm having to write an Arianna Grande bit and Tim Minchin bit for work. But it's a drag and I don't really want to do it. I go to Canberra and buy weed. The lady selects some for me, an assortment, and it's $20 total. Some of the weed is long stalks with purple flowers. I'm back home. I hide the long stalks upstairs in my room in my parents house, but now it's Alex Muller's room and it's messy full of clothes. I try to find the rest of the weed and look at the back of the car but can only find bags full of forgotten items, like a bag that contains a fancy handbag.  I'm at a pool. It starts off being an inside pool. I get in and butterfly to the end. Then I freestyle back but it hard to lift my left arm. Then I'm in a street. I come across a Asian old guy who has tokens for good and bad luck. We take turns flicking the colours to each other. He flicks me all white tokens for good luck. I flick him white tokens, then come across a black token, and then he watched me as I flick that into the gutter instead of towards him. He's pleased and he tries to tell me something, I think about a good luck ritual he wants to perform, but the words are garbled. I'm confused as I leave.  I get back to the pool and it's an outside pool now. The pool attendant who is a friend of mine is locking up, putting metal gates around the pool. I've come back fir my mobile phone, which I put in a shoe. The guy is carrying several mobiles but mine isn't there.

I'm in a supermarket and two ceramic plates we are buying have broken in the trolley. We're at the cashier and my husband Dan goes to look for more, but there aren't any. I later look for plates online but can't find them.

I'm in a bar with some guys and some friends. One of them, a white guy, argues with me about the existence of God. He's a believer. I argue that a fair and benevolent God couldn't put people through terrible trials in their life. The guy sitting on the other side of me who is black, agrees with me and adds his own arguments.  Someone orders food and drinks and it arrives. But it's expensive as happy hour has passed. There's some prawn noodles.  I'm in my flat, but realise I have a clash with two people staying over the same night. I tell Dan of this dilemma.  A room called Nightingale.
I feel so embarrassed when I send out a film audience feedback survey for a film that is already complete and screening
My nose is bleeding, both nostrils, streaming down. But I'm not worried as it's a sign.

Making a dress, black/ navy fairly basic but functional design. Staff were making these, one at a time & when the next dress was ready to be sent to the next floor, the ? would not work.... nothing could be delivered. We were trying to find why it was not working and how we could fix it.

I was with Val & I had a free sort of computer tablet thing to slot into computer.  It was the size of mobile phone & I had tried it & was showing it.  Worked well & happy but wondered to Val what this other bit was used for.  There was an extra piece.  She was not sure & reluctant to try. I was going to be swayed by her, then just tried this thing & wow it enhanced photos.  The holly & berries looked amazing.  I showed Val.  I said I am so glad I tried this bit.

I was with a group of about 10 people my age group & we all had deep skinny wire trolleys with possessions in them. Piled up but with order. We were waiting, kind of herded together. My cousin Ruth was there too & I said to  her "Why are we waiting?" She was accepting.  I asked " Where are we going ? & why ?" She shrugged. I looked at the people all standing & said to Ruth "Let's go by ourselves now" She was slightly hesitant but we started to slowly move away from others and we were discussing which was the best way to go.

I was with a group of 4 lots of people. We were on a grassy walkway beside a beach. Flat & we all were walking big dogs. I was with a partner ? and we had to segregate into one of each of 4 groups.  It spelt out some 4 letter word. I was comfortable with this arrangement & my partner was also. Each of us were. We were a far distance from each group. I said "we need to begin to walk soon.  I feel slightly nauseous but it's something I can deal with.

I was looking for a flat to stay in for some months in Paris.  I was there for work & a man was escorting me to places to look at. I looked at one & said to my assistant, I guess this will be ok, only for a few weeks/months. I felt accepting this when the escort who had not pressured any decisions thus far said "Come stay in my home. It is in the centre of Paris" "No, I don't wish to be a guest" I struggled with what I needed to say. He then said" But it has a piazza & the home surrounds this" "Sounds wonderful I will come & see ok " I nod to my assistant & we walk to this big door, that opens into a beautiful huge courtyard, with palms & space and i would have my own apartment. Perfect  I agree this is it ...  Later I am walking with "family" at a beach ..it is spacious & 2 people are walking slightly behind me. One is tall & other is short.  I am wearing those huge sunglasses that I had desired & feel the part. I am in charge here....I have the means to make my own decisions.  However they are giving advice on what area, what style of place to live in. Inside I feel so overwhelmed by the dominance but I must listen to their views... keep my mind open. The smaller one becomes more persistent &  .I think enough !  "No I will look here & I will decide. Thanks" They are miffed but it is my choice.

I was working with accounting discrepancies. The female boss was big noting herself trying to "correct" it talking to the programmers. She'd come back to me with a note try this or that This went on for a while back to the programmer to me. I had already looked at all she was talking about & most was not a program error. She was holding this slip on paper with 3 lines on it, that she was trying to tell me how to do it. Didn't work, I said "Can I call the programmer & speak directly to him"  She snatched the piece of paper from me & said No  I was a bit surprised but not. Then she said " Well if we cannot solve this we can delete it out " I was mortified & said so firmly " No way. I'd rather carrying this on the books forever than delete it  " I turned to the male boss who was looking over her shoulder & he nodded in agreement to me. I said "That would be committing a fraud "

DD_problematicSR_why: 1st dream but SR apply to all dreams
Text: Like a school with lots of rooms, open no one in them. I was sorting out my pandemic plan, we all had to. Coded areas. All mine were sorted but I mucked around not sure & I wanted to put the red spotted bird button I make in one area. I did, then took it out but no I felt this was my plan & this has meaning for me. So the red button bird stayed in & I was happy & confident when I explained, no one ? my choice.

At Robin's, we'd met in city as i had travelled in from country area. We went to his house as I was sleeping there that night. We'd been dozing on the ? train & then reached his place. It was a man's sparse odd house. Raised from the ground but not second story. I always "trusted" Robin but I also did not, always an under current. I went to put my things in my room & I was careful not to look much but did think it odd to have a double bed & a single squashed in room. But that really was Robin. I went into living area after peeking out the side of the blind where I saw daylight peeking through. Robin when I walked in to the kitchen was preparing our meal.

I was in different flats, first was this spacious unfurnished one above the carport style...older flat & someone was with me looking. I took it like i was being sort of relocated ? Then I we met by Tony an ex work colleague of years ago & I was moved again. Jan another ex colleague of same era praised my hard work which I felt meant something but not as much as a home & not having to move anymore. I moved close by in a white unit, which I was told I'd have to relocate next door as this one was due for renovations & the one I was moving to would be finished. I was happier about that..I moved & felt "settled" but the renovator was parked over both carport spaces which were separate from the building. So I had to ask him with my male friend beside me now not doing anything except being a presence. The renovator was obliging. Then 2 other more public radio known people parked in driveway & I thought this is so inconsiderate & by now I was kind of angry because so many stupid disruptive things I had to deal with.

Brad & I came across each other by chance in a city ? He was keen to meet up after our other commitments to catch up on our lives, I was too. He gave me an address to call to which I assumed was where he was staying for the work stuff. It was a large office like building with concrete ramps & sides winding up around this tiered buidling. Odd place reminded me of office block I worked in in Canberra. Inside the building was 80's style with lumbering big dull green benches, in an office foyer. Brad is his welcoming warm self & I am entered into the "Home" I was stunned & felt weirdly uncomfortable. Intruding. I shrugged & took it as I found it. He was babysitting 2 of his pre school aged children & they were asleep, I was uncomfortable now on alert. I felt myself become reserved, cautious but also open & friendly as not to give him the impression of what I was seeing did not belong to the man I knew . I was silently observing him. We talked of nothing of ourselves. He then seemed to be sitting behind a huge office desk. A work situation.of powerful old public service bosses. I decided it was time to go back to where I lived & as I was getting ready to go one of his children a boy about 5 had woken up & was laying on a couch, very engaging & chatty.  I thought you are like your father, nice kid. Brad was uncomfortable but I just talked to the boy politely & explained I was going now. Brad walked me to the door in his polite warm way. He was angling to meet up again & decided he'd walk down the now a country lane to my car.  It was daylight too. The questioning became Robin who was a man who was silent & ? he asked what I was going to do now... I am driving to city to footy match & then back to xyz for ? He was surprised & when this happened his body would react but nothing else did. I left and felt kind of sad the meeting with Brad was not the man I had once held in awe.'

I drove out of regional city through a sparse pine forest area to a glen where a community lived & I was to meet a group of craft peopl. The lady I was to meet was in an older style house & vintage furnishings and crockery. The house was cluttered, messy & unkept. The lady was biggish and of her own self importance, who ruled her family on her tongue, bossy & important. An adult daughter sat back a bit from her mother... I thought oh play along with this you will be ok & not here for long. I'd been left alone in their kitchen & I thought this is dirty. I don't like being here. I stood reluctant to go join them outside. I took a cup from a green set to talk to the lady about, have some common ground. But she fondled it but really had nothing to add. She sat with her family with things surrounding her apart from the rest of the group of younger women. She was holding a baby. With all this stuff around her. I knew she had had grief in her life & gave her that leeway . I had not been introduced to anyone ..so I amused myself watching a small animal in dirt which then was replaced by a tiny child who wiggled out from it's mother's care...then it really moved fast & I was astounded no one was watching , so called out to the Mum one of 2 talking & laughing together...your baby has raced towards the front gate. Yes they laughed & didn't move. I thought no-one here cares about anything but themselves. I am going now & left.

i was wearing a new off white dress, that was a style I had worn in late 1960's I felt good in it & I was out of my jeans etc..Going to some party function thing in small town. Numbers were limited & I'd been invited & felt special. My friend Lorraine asked me to call in on way out to show her the dress. She had a group of her crony friends with her & everyone looked & I felt very uncomfortable, I didn't like this at all. Lorraine's dog was suddenly shoved onto my chest by Lorraine and the dog had wee'd all over my new dress. I was mortified & then so upset. Everyone laughed. I thought stuff you lot. I tried to wash it clean but I was soggy & soaked & no one offered me a towel etc..... So I had to change from my dress.... & went back to say goodbye & Lorraine had heard someone couldn't attend so wanted to be the person to come ...I said not my call. So she rang & got the ok & sidled up beside me to come with me. I thought after all you have done to me you think this is ok...not my friend just a spiteful lady.

Groups with 4 categories & 4 groups & some adhered to what was required ..others did what they wanted to do & tried to justify it.... I kept watching all this in disbelief... But decided our group would do as asked. It was so annoying watching others do this with disregard I spoke up ....

Teaching craft in a huge house with huge rooms. This couple had asked me to do a class for them. It was shortish notice but easy so accepted. A girlfriend & I turned up to a room full of ladies ... I set the people on a creative course & I observed. All completed at end of day.... everyone was doing their own thing at their spaced out tables, content. I walked thru the other rooms as was curious to see what others were doing. Then packed up my gear including a large awkward display board. I was eager to leave & I needed to be paid $3000.00 for the class. Suddenly the couple had slipped out of sight, I had known this to happen before so went searching for either of them. No luck I was feeling angry & would bill them but when I do a class I expect to be paid at time. So I was pretty annoyed & said so to my friend. On leaving they appear with a group of women so I ask up front for payment, polite but I had an audience. I was paid. It felt scummy. I don't like that treatment, the deceit leaves me cold.

I was with my long term partner & he was someone I trusted..I had gone out of the unit to see what some noise was and saw 2 police on the street and they saw me & suddenly I was being quizzed about my partner & ?. I had no idea what they were asking I came back indoors & asked my partner what that was about. His mate had been in a bit of a "spot" & he'd helped him, then bought him back here. I was alarmed , how serious was this .The police have been very heavy handed so may be nothing but could be something if they decided... The police were now searching for my partner, so I got him into the unit next door which was already searched & no one was living there full time. Then I planned our escape, down the laneway & never to return as my partner could have been taken wrongly. So we ran away.

I was putting pattern sample squares into categories of same.  Fabric ones some were oblong & some square & differing sizes Others were of ? But 2 boards & they looked good I thought.  They has meaning to me. Male colleague was critiquing them for some marks & he was being picky, & it annoyed me because I thought it was unnecessary. In the end I moved a few around shuffled them & he passed it. I was thrilled

I was working with other people in a large warehouse room. The work was cutting up stuff it was precise, measured & exact work. I was very aware this was critical to the job. Co workers were friendly but we were busy. Then there was an after social event where I with my partner & family were meeting up at a large shopping strip to eat. We needed to bring own food & things to eat off etc. I was getting organised & I was also hungry. We drove there to meet with another 2 sets of families who I knew but not well. It was a bit of confusion for me as I was worried ...how would I fit in, I was nervous, I wanted to have more details to do this. We were shown to our table which was picnic style white painted... like a huge sort of open air cafeteria. People were about sitting but not close. I needed to go & get my food from the car & use the toilet. As I set out in a rush a lady plonked in a single chair in a strange spot by herself & appeared to be waiting for someone. She was middle ages 50 ish frumpy & dropped her cardigan & biggish handbag beside her on the floor. This made me alter my course quickly to not trip over the stupid woman.I felt irritated. She smiled half embarrassed nervous smile & I suddenly felt sorry for her feeling uncomfortable so smiled back & kept going.  The being with people I did not know well on an outing gave me a feeling of apprehension, on alert to how I should behave to fit in.

I was in the bush with my partner. I noticed the wind rustling the leaves of the trees in front of us. I asked him whether we were on Wiradjuri country and he said yes. I tried to remember how to speak Wiradjuri so I could speak with my ancestors. I wanted to show my partner how ancestors show that they’re listening, that they’re there but I couldn’t think of how to speak Wiradjuri. I could only think of the word “garru” (magpie). I wondered whether my nan would hear me and whether she’d know what I was saying in Wiradjuri because she didn’t speak it. I wondered if our ancestors would teach her. I felt upset that I couldn’t remember how to speak with her.

I was at a place that had Aboriginal cultural significance - it was a giant rock with carvings, and I walked underneath it into a museum. Someone was chasing me and I was trying to get away. There was a woman who worked there who thought I was going to steal something. Then I was with Danielle and Alex. We were kids, and we were trying to climb through windows. Something happened that made me feel self conscious about being bigger than them. Then I was somewhere else being chased again. It looked like a town made of shanties, and it was like I was in the middle of a war. There were guns firing and I had to run down streets without being shot. At one point there were a few women and for some reason I had to lock them up. I put them in a big black sack and there was a mechanism to lock it that I spent time trying to work out. They were crying and screaming. There was dog poo on the ground. At some stage I was running again and I was on a hill covered in trees next to a highway. A man on a motorbike came towards me- I knew him and felt relieved. At some point I was out with my brother and dad. It was late. We were inside somewhere but not at home. Me and dad were hungry and my brother and I shared a pizza but it was smaller than I was expecting and dad ate most of it.

I was trying to get to school on time. I was running and felt stressed but I couldn't make my legs move fast enough. Then I remembered I have a car and found it on a street. There were kids, Sophie's children also getting to school. Then I was in a classroom. It looked old fashioned, and the tables were arranged into long rows. Sophie was the teacher. At one point I was outside of the class with some boys and we ran back to class and realised we were late. I didn't want to go inside and get in trouble so we sat in the doorway. There were other kids spilling out into the doorway sitting cross-legged. The kids were primary school aged, and sometimes I was too and sometimes I was an adult. I was sitting at a desk and there was a boy nearby who had been mean to me. We moved positions and I had to sit next to him and I didn't want to. Then Uncle Pat was there and he announced that a man had died. Everyone was sad. Emily and I were then in a bathroom and she told me that the man who had died had molested her. Then I was having a conversation with Sophie. I can't remember the details but she said something like "well, you can just go to TJ's house" and I said, "no, I should just go to your house, you live closer" and she seemed surprised and laughed.

I was watching this situation like a film but I wasn’t directly involved. There was a blonde girl and she was running from something. It was night time, dark and wet. She was overseas, somewhere in Europe and the road was cobblestone. She was young and she only had a small backpack. At one point she met a tall young guy and pulled him into an alleyway to have sex. There was a man that was helping her when she got in trouble and would book her a flight or get a helicopter to pick her up. She was scared and running and she called him and he said he’d get her on a flight out of where she was. She arrived in another town and was in a flat with two other girls who seemed annoyed to see her. They were showing her the bedroom she would sleep in. The blonde girl said she’d have something to eat and one of the housemates said “you’re not eating in your bedroom” and the blonde girl said “yes I am”.

I was somewhere with Scott waiting for the footy to play on a big screen. I asked Scott where he wanted to stand to watch and he pointed to a spot near the back and I was surprised and a bit annoyed because I didn’t think I’d be able to see and I knew he was not wanting to be near the front because people from work were coming and he was feeling socially anxious. Ollie was there but he was younger and I kept giving him cuddles. Phil arrived and I commented that his hair looked good and he laughed and made a comment about how if you gel your hair it hides your bald spots.

I was swimming in the ocean surrounded by rocks and saw someone else swimming. I realised it was Tanya (friend from work). I was a bit embarrassed because I was in bathers and she seemed very surprised to see me.

I was sitting on the floor of an unfamiliar room, my legs stretched out in front of me. There was no carpet or rug covering the wooden floor boards, and the light coming through the tall windows was quite bright. My chest was covered but I wasn’t wearing a shirt, and I was looking down at my belly, aware that I was pregnant. By concentrating, I was able to advance the pregnancy within a few minutes to almost full-term.

I was walking around a city which I didn’t know, and as far as I could tell, I was the only one there. Everything looked only very recently abandoned, if at all, as if everyone had simply disappeared within seconds. I came across a cafe specialising in ice cream; round, black, rickety metal tables were arranged outside on the pavement with mismatching glasses and bowls in threes upside down. I sat down in one of the chairs, and a woman came out of the cafe. She was Italian, quite elderly, and after a little conversation she started serving me ice cream. One scoop in each bowl, one strawberry, one vanilla, and one chocolate. The strawberry ice cream was in a metal bowl, and it was so cold that ice formed on the outside. I scratched at it with my nail to make marks, and I was reminded of an episode of Morph which I had seen early in my childhood. Morph eats an enormous amount of ice cream out of a metal bowl bigger than him, and becomes so cold that he freezes solid.

The characters Sirius Black and Remus Lupin were in a Western setting. Remus was living in a one-room wooden cabin in the middle of a prairie, dusty, yellow light. Sirius was on the run from the law, though innocent as in the books. As he approaches the cabin in search of a hiding place, Remus greets him by pointing a pistol in his face; he’s not sure if he can believe that Sirius is completely innocent, and they haven’t seen each other in years— but they somehow end up in bed anyway. ‘Mystery of Love’ by Sufjan Stevens is playing quietly in the background.
There are some trees, or tree stumps seems more accurate, and they are really leaning. Like too far over. And I have to try to level them up.

I was in a large house, with lots of people. Some of these people were on my ‘team.’ They helped me, or gave me directions, such as to climb a ladder and open a hatch door onto another floor of the house. I could see the feet of someone in that room, but it was important that they not see me. Then I was on my own, walking in countryside - dry countryside, but in winter. I was listening to a portable radio, and I had a rucksack on my back. On the radio, I heard the voice of my team leader back at the house - a woman called Georgia. On the raido she was speaking to me, and I missed some of the message, so I re-wound it to listen to it again. By this time I was in a city, and I knew that I was somewhere between Kurdistan, Iraq, and Syria. In the radio message, Georgia told me to go to ‘the front.’ I wasn’t sure where that was, and I didn’t know if it was safe to ask anyone. So I walked. As I walked down a busy road, I became aware of reaching a border. It wasn’t a proper border with checkpoints - I just knew that I had crossed over one, on this busy street.

the same group of people were with me throughout. I didn’t know them well - they seemed like people I had only met recently, but we had joined together for some purpose. sleeping - we did a lot of it. me and one other member of my group. For economy we both slept on the same bed, and I seemed to keep losing things down the side of the bed. I was sharing the bed with a man, handsome, very nice. I was aware that he was attractive. Somehow the next thing I remember is standing with a group of people, congratulating a woman for achieving something. She was wearing a pantsuit, and standing next to her youngest son, who was adopted. He was wearing a karate outfit and he had ginger hair. The woman was telling us that she never really achieved anything with her life, but the ‘host’ of whatever this was reminded her that she had raised two wonderful sons, one of whom was this adopted son. She had also met Michelle Obama once, through the work she did. The point seemed to be that she obviously *did* achieve things with her life.

squatting behind a vehicle, changing my menstrual cup. It’s not ideal. Then I was in training to be a coach driver. I was on the coach, learning how to count passengers, read tickets. There were two coaches, and I was meant to be driving one of them. The driver who was training me showed me everything, including how to count the different ticket types. I was worried about this - I didn’t think I could count three different things at once. The different types had different coloured print on them - green, yellow, or red. He told me to do one last count of my coach and we would leave. My coach was full so it was easy to count - 40 people. I stepped off the bus, then got back onto it. When I did, I saw that some passengers from the back row were different - instead of three people, there were two young women lounging in the back row. When I asked to see their tickets, they sighed dramatically and got them out for me. They were laminated pieces of card on rings, and I had to flip through them repeatedly to make sure I found the information I needed. After confirming the women were ok to be on board, I stepped off the coach to tell the other driver. I couldn’t find him. And then both coaches pulled away without me. I chased them, slowly - they were in traffic - but he wasn’t driving the other coach, and my coach was in the faster lane. I knew where we were going but i wasn’t going to catch the bus in time. Then I was at a place called Hampton Court Palace. My friends Bex and Rob, who had been in the coach caper, were there now, too. There were two horses we were looking after? One looked very ill. Someone seemed to expect this. my breathing wasn’t right.

I was with my friend Matt, who I haven’t seen since we were in high school, nearly twenty years. He put on this technology - in the dream it was referred to as bionic, as being a bionic man or something - they looked a bit like advanced leg braces. And they made him fly. Not far, and not very high, but just enough to sort of glide over where we were, which was a city next to the sea. It looked a bit like downtown Melbourne. I got to try the bionic braces on. I don’t remember flying, but I think I must have. we heard a song being played, a really familiar song, like a classic Motown record. But it was being played in a different time signature, and I asked Matt, ‘Do you hear that? Is that in 5/6? Or 6/8?’ But he couldn’t, or wouldn’t, answer me. Then, somehow, my friend Lucy was there and we were talking about babies. Matt was maybe still there. And someone sounded surprised when I said I had had a baby. They wanted to know where it was. I said it was in Australia. It wasn’t really mine - either I had given it up for adoption, or I had been a surrogate. Or I just gave it up. But I didn’t miss the baby. I remember a feeling of being unusual for all of this. Then I am standing at the side of a busy road, wearing a face mask. I run across the road, and almost get hit by a white van - I keep saying sorry to the driver, who can’t see me saying it because of the mask. But he isn’t angry. I keep running.

I am in a structure that looks like a castle turret - it’s made of stone and has winding stairwells. I go from level to level as everyone else is ‘finishing,’ but I’m not sure what it was they were doing.  But I have papers with me, with everyone else’s names and work and marks on them. School work? But everyone is an adult, and it seems as though they are in teams. Some of the teams are having a dispute amongst themselves. I keep travelling. I find a hidden stairwell with a low ceiling, with which to move between levels.  Then everyone is trying to get out of the building. Then I am in a different kind of building, interacting with some of the same people. solving some sort of problem.

I was with my good friend, Pippa, but she was behaving strangely. At some point I was avoiding her instead of being with her. Later I was walking to the Polish embassy. I ran into a woman who was lost, but she was also looking for the embassy. She had a car, so I offered to get us there together if she would give me a ride. She was very nice. She was applying for the same job that I was applying for, and I felt competitive, but I helped her anyway.  my job. lifting boxes of honey onto and off of a truck.

I was mostly inside this building - one of those buildings with lots of glass, and steel struts. It was bisected down the middle with this corridor - like a covered walkway or drive. It was just wide enough for a car, and there were double doors at either end. My mother was parked at one end, outside the doors. It was an odd place to park. It was a Toyota Rav4. I didn’t see her much, or possibly at all. She had cancer. At one point, the postman tried to get through the double doors. He was driving something like a tank, not a normal postie car. He tried to push the doors inwards, when they normally push outwards. Inside the building, there were little cafes, but also other things - businesses, or small shop maybe. It looked a bit like the glass bits of Borough Market. There were stairs and a lift, and I gave people directions to somewhere they were going downstairs. I said you can use the stairs to the right, or the lift to the left. Even so they struggled to work out where they were going. One of the people was a Dutch man I met on holiday many years ago, with whom I had a brief romance. He didn’t seem to remember me, but he did keep wandering over to where I was. At one point I was back on the street where I grew up, outside my mother’s house. I was in front of our neighbours’ garden, and I found a Destroying Angel mushroom. I had to look it up just to check I had identified it right. The photo I found of the mushroom in a book/online looked precisely like the photo I had taken. When my neighbour emerged from his house, I walked away quickly so he wouldn’t see me.

I remember a sort of terraced set of open rooms, with washing machines in the corners. I must have been in charge of them, because when there was water on the floor, I thought it was my fault. It wasn’t just a bit of water on the floor - it was ankle deep, at least. Then I could tell it was draining out somewhere, the water level was going down. Someone I knew was there, and she had simply removed something that had been caught in a drain. At some point, I am hanging out with Brad Pitt. No idea what we were doing. He mentioned he wanted to get the rights to some song, and he made it sound like he wouldn’t get permission. I then re-told this story a number of times to other people. Civilians. I kept repeating to them the phrase: ‘You’re Brad fucking Pitt.’ As though it was obvious that he would be granted permission to use a song for whatever his purpose was. No one I told the story to was interested, or at least no one seemed to join me in the ‘yes, it’s obvious that famous people get what they want’ sentiment. The last fragment I remember: I was wearing gloves because my hands were covered in some sort of biting/stinging insect. I had to prove it to someone, so I removed one of the gloves, and the insects went straight for my skin. The pain was intense but not impossible.

I was with a group of people, next to a floor covered in white powder. It was meticulously smoothed over, so when someone walked over it, it was quite obvious. I chose not to walk on it. There were consequences for those who did. I felt smug about being innocent.
I was with people who were on my MA course. I felt very strong social anxiety around them. I was attributing the anxiety to menstrual cramps, though I sort of knew it wasn’t just the cramps.
a different existence in a parallel universe containing some of the elements of this world and also some different. university people like lecturers and teachers and friends from university.

solving different parts or tasks of something - then chased around a garden and outdoor area -almost like an obstacle course or athletic track crossed with a rose garden. Then being in teams for a university class in German - and I am not on a team with any of my friends.

being invited to someone's party and graduating in pink high heels and running across a road in a busy city full of traffic. I talk to my friends about eating out and how it makes a nice change from buying lots of ingredients for one meal. At the party running up and down the staircase of the four storey house and trying to remember which bathroom to use because of health and safety guidelines. Then leaving the party early and walking down a steep hill in the London borough I grew up in and briefly talking to a cardinal about Pride and prejudice and then about to go on the tube when I see a dog running away from a levitating horse's head and I hear people say how strange things are nowadays.

living in France in an alternative reality with older sister and younger brother in a large château and re-decorating my new room for when my friends come over. Also a history lesson and talking to a punk local guide about her cheese company.

About my brother marrying one of our close childhood friends. Also about me sharing a flat with one of our close childhood friends - a sort of whitewashed flat with pot plants and lots of tea and a kettle. Then I know a guy who can't afford a school trip to Prague but he steals along anyway and so do I and we end up at a café with giant pot plants and décor like the 1890s - Art Nouveau swirls and people in period dress and one of the waiters is the German actor Daniel Bruehl who we speak German with and dance to jazz music. Walking round narrow colourful streets of Prague and comparing it to Paris but the people are different and also I can't think of the main sights to see in Prague, compared to Paris.Also watching videos by film students about train journey to Edinburgh.

having a conversation with my Romanian ex-co-worker while we clear tables and also about watching a promo video for a wine made in Berlin talking about the main wines and vineyards along rivers in German and seeing my cousin’s vlog. Also being in town with my brother and my friends and parents and seeing a semi-fascistic/nationalistic army procession so we come home quickly and me and my ex-co-worker speak to a Romanian lady and her kid in a wood and afterwards we lock up the home and secure it and hide in the cellar. Also spending time with a group of Germans from a student eco group. Also trying to cork an open bottle of red wine and spilling some red wine.

Going to a ski/snowboard centre where the snow is melting and I try to stop it melting and try to speak German. Also taking a unit in Politics at university and forgetting how hard academia is and I receive my essay back and the feedback is that my essay is not academic enough apparently.

Telling a dream I had to a fictional coworker at the hotel where I work and we are standing at the hotel bar, except the bar looks different like a dimly lit New York bar instead and it is the depth of winter and very dark and cold and then I am serving some wine and champagne to customers and am asking the head of wine at my workplace a question. Then I am talking to my parents about Winston Churchill and my brother is talking about going back to school/university - while this conversation is happening I am rearranging the objects in my bedroom and then I am driving a car across the moors alone and I am remembering how to use the pedals and gears.

possibly going on holiday somewhere and looking at overexpensive gold and silver jewelry souvenirs in a shop at the airport. Talking to the friend who had his birthday today or yesterday  about his embarassing birthday stuck in a tree and also speaking to one of my coursemates from French and German about something to do with university or someone we both know. I arrive back in Bath after my holiday and walk along the toffee coloured Georgian streets.

our family going through all the artwork we have in the house, because we have too many paintings etc. and my brother wants to put some of his photos up on one of the walls. A friend/ex-housemate from 2nd year turns up at our house in a bad way with dope on him and is very stoned/drunk etc. My parents try and talk to him, while I tell him I don't want him here, but in the end we give him a bed for the night and I try to hide the fact he is so high/drunk from my parents. My brother tries making a cocktail from an Italian cocktail book - oranges, lemons and something alcoholic that looks like an Aperol Spritz. Also my friends from London are in the dream - we are all in London or another big city and it has something to do with being at uni or doing a masters.

being back at university and living in a sort of underground bunker with lots of space and light. I have some friends round. It rains and it transpires we have a submarine which we transfer to. Also trying to make friends with foreign students unsuccessfully- trying to make friends with a Catalan girl and a Japanese girl joins a friendship group led by a cool Chinese guy who heads a K-pop group called Easy Girls.

living in a country run by two rival companies – Magfakesque and Hispanigan. The 2 companies are locked in an industrial and civil war. I go for a coffee with my brother at a bar then later on with a woman I’ve worked in a charity with again. I arrive in a plaza/square with some uni friends later on when we hear weapon fire and explosions and see smoke. So I flee for the border with Zazarive the next country along which I have residency for and cross. I am arrested for illegally crossing by a border guard then am rescued by a bona fide border guard who lets me seek asylum.

buying bars of soap at a hotel and leaving in a lift where social distancing is not observed and then going onto the New York subway where I confront a guy bullying someone else. The guy I confront apologises to me. Later,  at the house - a big New York brownstone house - shared with my siblings, on one evening it is dark and snowing. In the house are me, my siblings and their partners- I watch the yellow windows of neighbours from our garden windows, while I am waiting for a message from an artist friend who lives opposite. We decide to invite an old friend to dinner. We say goodbye to him as heavy snowfall begins- my siblings want to play in the snow, but I stay inside. Later on, our parents join us for a music session playing guitar and two family friends talk about a mask making factory taken over by Extinction rebellion activists.

Working in a hotel/retreat for female guests – sort of like yoga with health garden etc. and having an important VIP author to stay but she is a bit disappointing and American, as well as having candid conversations with different age groups. Also about directing a film about 4 fairies who are friends with a depressed human who commits suicide because his soul belongs to a departed fairy. Watching a video for a rock song.

encountering a malicious ghost/poltergeist in a forest with one of my friends and then later at a past-student party organised by one of my student friends I faint and refuse to believe in the ghost’s existence although my friend believes it to be real and meets an old lady at the party to talk about the ghost with. Also writing an essay about this ghost using notes for Russian and East European books. Also speaking French with a guest and making morphine.

going to a friend's house in France and how she lives in a massive chateaux and makes me feel inadequate about my own house etc. Her house is stunning and pale lilac with flowers and plants everywhere. talking falcons and exploring a wonderland-like landscape.

I was in Eastern Europe somewhere. I was staying with people in different places within the one city, but not because they were already my friends but because we were all part of something I was coming to join in on. Each place was enjoyable for the new social context. The last two times though, something happened where a child or children had come to join us, and I played with them and ended up both wanting to keep them and having to - their parents disappeared or they said they didn't have any. The second time there were two small children, and when I picked one of them up there was something vampiric about it - either I was worried it was a vampire, or that I was and I wouldn't be able to control myself sucking its throat.

There was some big event or big conference/training event happening. I along with many other young people was in a new place, maybe a city, and we were doing lots of activities, visiting sites together, going for bike rides. A girl was living in a flat and I knew somehow that she had been unhappy there. She was moving out. I was going to stay there for the duration of the conference/training. When I got in there I immediately thought, no wonder she was unhappy here, it was one small room, with a kitchenette. I had hundreds of wine glasses with me, that I was in charge of bringing to some evening event.
