Mum and I were in Mauritius and there was a kind of basket thing you could sit in and turn a crank to move to get up the mountain. Mum said her sister was too scared to do it. We would do it the next day. Some lady was going to take us to do it the next day. My boyfriend from when I was in japan was with us. He seemed grumpy and he wanted his music on in the car. He gave me a tape to play, it played a song by doja cat called boss bitch. In the evening I slept next to him for a little bit. Then the next day I think he flew somewhere or me and mum did. Mum and I were in the supermarket near my house in japan but the store was messy and there wasn’t much food left. I bought fish and panko crumbs to make Katsu curry but mum insisted she told me she was going to make indian curry. So I went round the store again and she waited. I found some packets of noodles I liked so I bought them too. Then we were at my old secondary school for a concert. I was going to play in the second half or something so I needed to wait. My mum was talking to one of the other parents at the side of the stage and was getting agitated that I needed to wait. I tried to remind her that a concert was going on but she didn’t seem herself. The parents looked disgusted at her. One parent said in German “does her kid have any friends?” My mum sat down and started trying to hand out flyers to some kind of event. The first half of the concert finished and the parents left. The kids in the concert were left and the teachers made a few announcements. I interrupted and started crying. I told the other girls (I was in an all girls school) I was really sorry about my mum but she’d had cancer two times and she was still on chemo for her arthritis. I said that she wasn’t all there mentally and sometimes she didn’t make sense when she talked to me. I was crying a lot.

I was in a shower cubicle with a girl and a boy. They were facing away from me. My most recent ex, Neil got in the shower cubicle too. The girl and the boy left and Neil smiled at me and kissed me. Suddenly we were in my old university room together on the floor. My covers and pillow were on the floor too. We talked about getting breakfast and Neil suggested pancakes. I offered to make them but he joked about my cooking being bad. I was a bit upset as he had never tasted my cooking. He went and made the pancakes and I found some kind of memory stick. When he came back up with the food I asked him what it was and he said he’d show me after breakfast. We ate the pancakes and I expressed why I was upset at his prior comment about me cooking. We also talked about what happened while we were apart.

I was in my own apartment and it was messy. My parents were looking round my apartment for some reason. I went to visit my old university friends in their apartment with my friend from university called Micheal. I feel like Micheal was one of my most genuine friends in university. It wasn’t too awkward seeing my other university friends but I guess we weren’t as close anymore and we didn’t have anything in common.

I was walking along a country road, I passed an indigenous child and said hello, they said hello back. I came to a small shack on the side of the road. Then I was in the shack and Viet was telling me how to catch chickens. I had to flatten the chicken with one hand against the ground and then stroke its head with the other hand to subdue it and then

We were getting ready to go to a club. I was with Alison and lots of other people. I didn't know what to wear. I put on a long grey tweedy dress/pinafore and boots. I didn't know if it looked OK. Then I decided to have a shower so took all my clothes off and went naked to the shower rooms - we were in some sort of communal accommodation. As I got to the shower rooms there was a lot of soapy water with dark hair in it flowing out from the door. I thought that someone I knew was in there, someone quite glamorous. I slid open the door and found it was crowded with all the shower spaces occupied and more women around. The floor was covered with soapy, hairy water, the atmosphere was jovial. I commented on the fact that I had gone there naked, this was seen as quite funny. Then I wasn't in the shower rooms anymore, I was back with others and fully dressed, ready to go and I was wondering how much money to take with me. Alison had bought the ticket to the club so I owed her for that. And it said to bring at least £40 for somebody's birthday present. I didn't have that much so thought I should bring my card. I was wearing the grey dress which was a bit shorter now, and boots, but no tights and I thought I would get hot dancing so didn't need tights. Then there was something about footwear, Alison was going to wear something else on her feet that would be better for dancing.

I was in a street, very busy with cars and people. To my left a black family had stopped a car and some little boys were crossing the road (the traffic stopped to let them cross), they were very cute and were on their way to see some relatives. Later on I was curled up on a sofa with a man who I think was one of these boys but now grown up. I was asking him about what clothes he had been trying on that day (when I saw him crossing the road). We were happy and laughing.

I was on a train having sex with my husband. We were kissing a lot, it was incredibly passionate and intimate and we were very very turned on. He was about to enter me and I knew we would both orgasm instantly but then we realised some people were coming along the train towards our carriage so we had to stop and try to get dressed quickly. I couldn't sort my clothes out, they were all tangled up.

I was with Cathy and Chris, sitting with them in a corridor somewhere, I think we were in America where they live, and there were some other people there - another woman between me and Cathy and maybe my husband was next to me. Cathy was blond, she was showing me a scrap book of pictures and bits and pieces that were something to do with me, and clothes. We were talking about clothes and buying second hand clothes. We were talking about when she next comes to England and where she will say. I was really happy to see her and talk to her.

I was trying to find somewhere to park. All the car park spaces seemed to be for residents only. In another part of the same dream I was with some other people I didn't know well - I think there was a man that I was interested in, and another man who was disabled and I shook his hand, I made a point of shaking his hand because his hand was deformed and I wanted to show the other man that it didn't bother me. There was another woman there too. We were going to get into a flashy sports car, I tried to open it but I was on top of the car and as it opened the top moved up so I fell off, I laughed at this. We got inside the car which was more like a restaurant table inside, and we sat down to drink champagne. I opened the champagne and poured it into some glasses but I couldn't tell whose glasses I had filled and whose I hadn't.

Somehow I was being encouraged to go an watch Chris Evans five year old son in his first school play - I reluctantly went along. We were in a school hall where there was a barrier all around it with the parents standing outside the barrier, and to start with the children were outside the barrier too, to the left of where I was standing. To start with there were about 10-15 little children, in grey school uniforms and their parents were holding their hands to try to encourage them. Chris Evans was on the other side of the hall and kept going on about his little boy, "isn't he sweet, look at him, there he is, he's got a bandage round his knee" which was annoying me. But then some of the little boys got distracted and went off to play somewhere else and gradually there were no children left to join in. So some of the parents decided to do the play for them - I realised that this was going to be a lot more fun to watch the parents mess around than a group of little children that i didn't know. As the parents went into the arena to perform, it was more as if the play was actually going to be a mock football match. Some of the dads were wearing grey shorts like their children. I noticed that Paul Jones was among them, and that really perked me up - I tried to flirt a bit with him but he didn't notice. Also noticed a blond man who used to be a children's presenter on Play Away, and lots of other I didn't know. They were funny.

I was at a conference or some sort of work/college do and we were about to get ready for the conference dinner, other women were dressing up and I felt really low and didn't want to go as I didn't have appropriate footwear. I had been trying to wash some grey ankle boots that had mud on them and ended up flooding the kitchen because the sink I was using didn't have an overflow, and i didn't realise the water was flooding, and the boots got completely soaked, along with some other things and they were the boots I was going to wear, so now I didn't know what to wear. So other women were dressing in nice dresses - they weren't too overdressed, not ball gowns, but nice dresses that would have been the sort of thing I'd wear, but they had nice shoes on and I had nothing to wear on my feet. At this point we were all standing up, and there was a lot of milling around and a lot of people. Then I was somewhere else, a smaller room, and people were leaving to go to the dinner, there were fewer people and they were still trying to persuade me to go but I was saying I didn't want to. The group left, they told me the direction they were going in if I wanted to catch them up, it involved crossing a bridge (trying to cross a stream but the stones were wet and slippery). I was left in the room with one man, we talked for a bit and then I decided to go after the others. Went out into the street, it was dark, an unfamiliar town, I found the bridge, and was crossing it. The bridge seemed to have an inside and outside, and you could walk along either part. I was walking along the inside, the bridge was white metal, very ornate, but very steep and slippery and I had to hold on to the edge bits to stop myself from falling. Then I got to the centre of the bridge which was flat, and a beautiful ornate room/shop that sold confectionary. There was white decorations like ostrich feathers and fans, very beautiful. As I made my way through there was a very elegant woman sitting at the table and she asked if I was just walking through or if I was staying for dinner. I said I was sorry that I was just walking through, and she offered me a free piece of confectionary from a basket - there were chocolates and also some clear animal shapes. She said most people chose the chocolate praline but the clear ones were special, so I chose a clear pig (like a glass flat pig). I bit into it and it was so delicious, like fondant or praline, but completely clear. Then I was throwing over-ripe apples really hard down the other side of the bridge which was now a residential street. I threw them really hard so they smashed onto the road with a splat. The apples were green and red and yellow, and I could smell them. Then I did arrive at the conference dinner, the people I knew were sitting in seats like in a theatre, so I went to join them but felt embarrassed about my footwear. Two of the women were Indian Asian and were joking because of some trick that one of their mothers had been playing on her that involved the other one (something about a photograph). I thought it strange that the mother would want to do that. I felt ungainly and awkward during a lot of the dream.

I was in a bookshop, it was ordinary at first, but then I went further into it and was in a huge room. I looked up to the ceiling which was domed and blue, and very far away, I couldn't lift my head enough to see right to the top of it. The bookshop was also like a library, with tables for people to read. I was looking at big books on the shelves, art books - I was looking for something but not sure what. Someone came in with some really tatty paperbacks they'd found and asked if they belonged to anyone. One was a children's story, it was really damaged, yellow cover but damaged. This was mine and I took it but then realised I didn't want it and gave it back. I was a bit embarrassed by it, I wished it had been a more intellectual book. There were a lot of other people in the bookshop, but it was spacious and I was very happy there.

I was in a garden, the owner of the garden was saying that it was a double terrace property, because it had a small area of paving slabs and then a patio below it, she was saying it as a joke but that there was something in the Domesday Book about double terraced property and she was making a joke that her small garden was like this. But I was sitting on grass and I saw a grey tabby cat lying on the small upper patio, stretching out and then it rolled over and fell off the patio onto the one below (not a big drop, just a few inches) and then rolled down the patio all the way to the small flower bed at the edge. I found this very funny and laughed a lot. The cat ended up lying down near me and I noticed that behind the cat, next to my slippers which were there, was a tiny mouse and I wanted the cat to notice it. The mouse was tiny, about the size of a bee, and then a bee was there too and I didn't want the cat to chase the bee. Then I noticed on the grass around me there were a lot of small containers that had had honey in. There were a lot of insects around, some huge flying things and I was scared of them. If I flapped them away, they came back more and I was telling others not to flap as it made them come back. Then it turned out that a rich woman who was some sort of relative that the day before had been very welcoming of me (I was a child) was no longer interested in me and wanted a younger boy, and I was very upset. As he was getting ready to go to tea with her I hugged him and was going to tell him to do something bad but then didn't and just told him to have a good time. Another old woman relative was also going and she came passed and said something to me, my reply was "but you care about us" and then I burst into tears.

I was watching a fish in a hole. The fish was like it had been filleted and splayed open and fried but it was alive, and this was just what this type of fish looked like. It was gasping for air at the top of the hole - the hole was like a hole in a rock, but not sure what it was connected too. Now and again I took the fish out and put it on the ground because for some reason that was a good thing to do, but then it gasped for air again and I put it back in the hole, which had water in it, but it was still at the top gasping for air. Then another of the same sort of fish appeared from below it, also gasping for air and I knew there wouldn't be enough space for both of them and was worried about what would happen to them. There was also something about a colleague from work leaning over my desk and I pointed out that there were a lot of nail clippings on the desk (not sure if was my desk or just a desk, and it was incredibly cluttered) just where she was leaning - we were both disgusted by this.

I was outside, in a park, and gave an older woman who I respected a book I had been recording my dreams in. She flicked through it and gave it back to me without comment. I was disappointed so pressed her a bit. The book was like a hard-back diary with entries for each day, and my entries were very short - I commented that my dreams were a lot longer than this but I just wrote down key words, and she said that that was good to know because she couldn't understand them as they were so brief. Amongst the entries there were also poems.

I was walking through a park which was wooded in places. Lots of people around. I was walking in a straight line, regardless of what was in front of me and I found myself walking down a deep pit with water at the bottom and realised it was a hole that a family with children had dug (a bit like a hole kids might dig on a beach, but this was all grassy), I felt a bit daft but also had a chant going through my head - go through it, or go over it, or under it, or round it. Before I had got to the hole I had been carrying a version of "clackers", I was playing with them no and again and was very conscious that this would make everyone look at me as they were noisy and unusual. After I'd clambered out of the hole I came to a wooded bit with lots of logs and I tried to climb over but had to go around, and saw that inside there was what looked like a massive crate stuffed with rubbish and people were clearing it out, I went to join in. the final piece of junk/rubbish was a box of papers which turned out to be the transcript of a play by a comedy duo, and suddenly the big crate turned out to be a lovely old theatre which was now cleared of rubbish and the comedy duo were pleased to see their play script again and talking about putting the play on. The atmosphere of the theatre was cosy and I said that it was amazing that whereas before this was just full of rubbish now it was somewhere that I would want to sit down in. It didn't look anything like a theatre, it was more like a cosy cottage. Then there were younger people there who were my friends and were very drunk, one of them was leaning down from high up, supporting himself with one hand on a ledge and he was being leering and unpleasant so I went to move his hand which would mean he would fall, but I supported his weight so he didn't hurt himself but he was angry with me anyway. I helped him to lie down on the sofa. Then this scenario changed again, and amongst all the people there were my two uncles, both lying down in different beds/sofas and I was talking to them. a packet of photographs/postcards that said they were off a village I knew but they weren't very interesting.

I was watching a band perform, the musicians were in a sort of performance arena and I was just outside to the left. I'm not sure how many other people were watching but i didn't feel alone. I was looking in particular at the three guitarists to the left of the performance area. They looked very rock and roll, the middle one looked like Billy Idol, the one on the right had dark hair and looked more like a 50s rocker. They were playing hard, and all were sort of vibrating. There was some sort of silvery/black confetti falling. Then from outside the performance arena to the left came the main star, on ice skates, he skated around the arena and I kept thinking he was going to crash but he didn't, he skated all around and then entered the arena from the back. He seemed a bit of a joke, and I sensed there was animosity between him and the other performers. I wanted one of the guitarists to notice me, particularly the dark haired one, it was as if I knew him. They were all shaking and vibrating with the energy of playing, but it was as if the entire scene was vibrating, not just the players. Then I remembered that I was supposed to be measuring my pee so peed into a jug, there was a lot of it and it was pinkish in colour, and then I realised that one of the guitarists was drinking it and I felt guilty.

Katie was giving me some advice, telling me about a meeting she had been to. Then I was telling someone else about this conversation, and looking back through my notes to recall what she had said. Katie helping me with my phone, I was trying to do something with it, but couldn't put the numbers in.  I was driving a huge lorry and was finding it easier than I thought. I negotiated a tight corner very smoothly and felt pleased with myself. I waited for a cyclist to go passed before pulling out. I watched a woman fall and roll underneath a car, but she was fine and sat under the car quite happily. The lorry was a left-hand drive and it was like I'd hired it from Porto airport and realised I hadn't got the satnav out of the suitcase so would I know the way. I thought I would be OK, having made the journey many times but quickly got lost as was driving through the middle of a city. I couldn't find anywhere to pull over, but somehow managed to get the satnav out of the back of the car (sometimes it was a lorry, sometimes it was a car), and then started having an argument with my husband about what address to put in the satnav. I wanted to put the nearby hotel we usually put in, but he insisted on putting in "samvega*" which he said was the name of our landlord, but I kept saying we don't have a landlord, and i've never heard of samvega. My husband argued back to put samvega in (although he wasn't sure of the name, or how to spell it), followed by his name (although the name he told me to use was actually his son's name). I was getting stressed but also thought I should just do it to show him that the satnav wouldn't pick up either of those as destinations.

I  parked the car in a tight space, up a rough, unsurfaced road. When I came back, it was too wedged in for me to get it out, it was in a corner and I thought another car had been deliberately moved so I couldn't get it out. I was wondering if I could lift it out. It wasn't completely me, I think I was male. The car was blue and very boxy.

I was trying to catch a train with Judi. She was already on the train. I didn't have a ticket so had to buy one from an automated machine. I couldn't work out how to do it - it asked me where I was right now and I typed in Bishop Stortford but it didn't ask me where I was going to. The next question was something else, I can't remember what. Then Judi came rushing off from the train which was going to leave in a few seconds as she had to do something, and she was hurrying me along to get back on it before it went, I told her to just go and don't wait for me because it was going to take me longer than a few seconds to get my ticket. But I didn't know when the next train would be. I wasn't that anxious about missing the train, but frustrated that I couldn't work out how to use the machine. There were lots of people milling about. The entrance to the platform was narrow, and everything was quite dingy, grey and run down.

driving in a city, lots of cars, there was a white car parked in the lane in front of me and I had to pull out to get passed it and then I was in the wrong lane, and had to come back in and sort of pushed in but felt relieved that I'd done it quite smoothly and safely.

With people from work. One of them was driving a bus and was doing a very good job of parking it in a tight space. Something escaped from the bus and I grabbed it, it was like a person but made of twigs/branches, or one branch but with arms and legs, covered in moss. It was hard to hold on to, and I had to get a colleague to help, it was twisting and trying to get away but we managed to subdue it. I felt sorry for it, as we were trying to help. Then we were going into the building where the bus had been parked, there were several of us from the office and also with us was Kathryn, she was telling us that she was going into a meeting where there would be reporters and she would tell them about the bus and it would be a big news story. There was a discussion about who would be interviewed - Michelle who drove the bus, Sue for some other role in what happened. Someone else asked me if I was disappointed that I wouldn't be in the story, and I said no, not at all because I hadn't had a role and we are a team. I couldn't tell if I really was disappointed or not. I was talking to Sue about what she was going to say, she was excited and nervous about it.

I was driving and passed Viet walking back along the road. He had been to get something, and I drove passed him and then felt guilty that I should have stopped to give him a lift even though I was going the other way. I stopped, and there were a lot of things in the road - some sort of yellow cloth, like disused banners, and I was near a sort of barrier/border point though there wasn't anyone around. Then I could hear voices and realised it was Viet coming back but he had morphed into Jaine and Judi. I was pleased to see them.

I was alone at my parents house. It is at the end of a cul-de-sac. It was night-time, and a group of teenagers gathered at the other end, they were very noisy. I opened the curtains to look at them but was too nervous to shout. Another neighbour shouted, but they got noisier and there were more of them. It was something to do with lockdown/curfew. Then I saw two neighbours were walking towards them so I quickly went downstairs to go with them, but it turned out the neighbours were going to join them, not tell them to be quiet. When I got back in to my house I realised that two of the teenage boys had come inside and were hiding in the bedrooms, I went into my parents bedroom, the bedding was all piled up at the end of the bed, and a boy was hiding under a blanket, I dragged him up. I didn't find anyone in my brother's room, but there was another boy asleep in the small room that used to be my bedroom. They weren't any trouble, but I didn't want them there. the house wasn't my parents house anymore but sort of our house in Portugal but in a state of disrepair. My husband was working on it and he'd said two people were coming to stay but I wasn't sure who. Then two men appeared, they were a bit rough and grizzled, but very friendly and seemed kind. I still wasn't sure who they are or why they were here.

a neighbour making some food. There was a big pot of carrots with marrowfat peas in it, and then another pot of something, but also she was making chocolate sauce with twix and kit kats in, and this was being put in various containers including little plastic bags. There were some children around. I was in a bedroom with my husband, the door was slightly open and just outside the door was a clothes drying rack with clothes drying on it, the carpet just outside the door which was partly underneath the drying rack was peeling up, and Joao was outside trying to flatten the carpet without moving the drying rack. My husband was naked on the bed and wanting me to touch him but I was embarrassed because Joao was outside. Then there was something about our cat, and my husband got up to go out of the room and while he was out I sneaked a twix out of one of the bags of chocolate, and felt guilty about it. The room was no longer a bedroom, but a kitchen/dining room and there were other people in it.

Wandering around trying to find a toilet. At one point I joined a queue, we were in some sort of big office space. The queue was passed some people sitting having a meeting and I recognised people from work. I was carrying my pee-measuring jug and was embarrassed that others would see it. THere were loads of people around. Eventually I got to the front of the queue and we went through some doors into another space. In another part of the same dream I was watching a television, the film was interrupted by an advert for the original Star Wars movie, the sound was loud and I tried to turn it down as I was in a room full of people who were cross with the noise. Later I was in a rambling old industrial space, and it was like I was in a science fiction film. I was with a man who was escaping, and there was an announcement that there was a male intruder and he should be apprehended. A woman opened a door and saw us, she assumed I was one of them as the announcement had only been about a man, so she thought I was helping to apprehend him. In the process I took her gun and tried to hit her with it but I did it very feebly and she fell but then hit me hard with it. Then I was somewhere else and someone (an old woman?) was treating me, and I was OK. In another part of the same dream, I saw Mike (my boss) and he had taken my pee-measuring jug as he said he needed it, but I pleaded with him and he gave me a new one he had just bought, but it was no good but it only measured in 500ml divisions and I needed my one that measured in 50ml divisions - he agreed to switch jugs.

I was in the sea, on rocks or a wall, there was lots of debris in the water, it was quite unpleasant. There was a large black object, I wasn't sure if it was part of a dead creature or something man-made.

My friend who is a yoga teacher was holding a sale to encourage people to come to her yoga class and I went - it was in a residential house and there were lots of people there, it didn't seem very good, the things she was displaying or selling weren't interesting. Suddenly I remembered I was in quarantine and shouldn't be there, and panicked, I left, trying to keep my distance from other people but it was hard as there were so many people milling around. I felt really bad, guilty and like I was going to get into trouble. I was walking back along the street was seemed like Lewisham Way in south London, as it gets near to New Cross.

I had done something that upset my friend Judi and she wanted nothing more to do with me. I was very upset about this. I realised it was not solvable. I was thinking I would remove myself from the whatsapp group I'm in with Judi and Jaine but I knew that once I did that I would never be able to rejoin. I was absolutely gutted. Then Judi morphed into my husband - it was he that I had upset and who was now completely blanking me. I was standing next to him at a food counter and he was ignoring me, it was horrible. Then I was in our neighbour Pete's house, he was offering me a room to stay in. I didn't want to take it up because I don't like him anyway but also because my husband hates him and would be very upset if he knew I was talking to him let alone living with him. I declined the offer. There were lots of other people in the house too, and it was crowded and untidy.

It was night and I was in a situation that was a bit scary and sinister. It involved trying to avoid being seen. Then at some point I was being asked to clean up an outdoor area, and was vacuuming it - it was like a yard with flower beds, and was quite dirty and wet. I didn't think I should use the vacuum cleaner, I thought I should use a dustpan and brush instead and although there was one I couldn't get it to work, or I couldn't get it to sweep, and ended up going back to the vacuum cleaner which worked but some parts were too wet and I was worried the vacuum cleaner would break.

Arrive at a hotel in the country on a hill. Big imposing building. Supposed to be very expensive. Seem to be with a group and a man I don't know. Reception area is closed off with plastic sheeting. Seem to be renovating. Small desk where we are ignored because the man and woman behind the desk are busy cutting up cheese and putting pieces into small ziplock bags. We are offered a bag of cheese each. I ask for a blue cheese too and a girl in the group asks too. They give us mix of both. We then proceed to a another room and are told to collect our luggage and help ourselves to biscuits. We have to be out by 7:30. Plates of Arnott's biscuits everywhere. I take chocolate biscuits which I haven't eaten for years. Also some spicy biscuit that looks like ones my mother used to make. Have too many and nowhere to put them. The man I am with lines a hat with a clean handkerchief and I put them in there. Announcement that we have to leave as it is 7:30. Find my bag in a small cupboard. Feeling anxiety about getting out in time.

Seemed to at old workplace, Child Safety. Writing a report on returning a child to parent. Mother a history of childhood sexual abuse, working very hard to get life on track. Waiting for mother to come for appt. Adding to report on desk.Workplace now more like Centrelink.  Meeting at workplace. I am not included. See husband's car, grey Ford Falcon, in carpark so assume he is at the meeting. A younger me thinks about cousin who I liked. I am waving my hands in the air, painted findernails, lots of glitter in the air.  Workplace again. I am coping flack about allowing clients to eat in the waiting area. I explain they only eat in a special room but I am lying. I quietly put food remains in a rubbish bin.

In a large room waiting for friends near the entry. Meals, drinks being served. Lots of activity. Bright lights. I write on the floor in chalk and in large letters "You made me roar" and then repeat. It looks  obvious but no one notices. Large group of friends arrive- Rose, Andy, Garth and others- but they walk past me talking and laughing. They don't see me. Someone comes out- staff- and asks if the group of semi-nudists have arrived. I mention the friends and they confirm that that is the group. I go into a different room in search of them. There is a bar and a few older women wearing glasses with thick frames and droopy colourless dresses. They look up with shy smiles, a bit sad, lonely. One looks like Mary and I approach. She turns but it isn't Mary. I continue on into a room off the side where the group might be.  They are there laughing, drinking, partying. I stand at the door. No one notices me.

Seem to be in a workplace. Perhaps a teaching environment. In a staff room with other people. No one I recognise. Argument between two people gets heated. One assaults the other. Sympathy is with the perpetrator who is seen as unfairly provoked. Very frustrated and angry but isolates himself. Mediator/judge is needed and we are all to "give evidence". There are lots of discussions about this. Then we are sitting in a long room with individual seating along the sides and a long bench seat across the middle. We are dressed formally and take our seats with the perpetrator up the front and the victim at the back. Tense atmosphere. We are back in the staff room. The cleaning staff have decided to decorate and plan for a party after the hearing. There are Xmas decorations so perhaps close to Xmas. They are putting up lights and have a mysterious box with something new. This is a kind of booth with a small canopy.  We are summoned back to the long room. I am talking with a staff member who is expressing something very earnestly and arrive back late. I have to sit on the long bench with is low and uncomfortable but feel I should be up the front with the perpetrator. Then we are all back in the staffroom. The party has begun. The booth is for dispensing different pasta sauces. An Indian man is in charge and persuades us to have big helpings of food. Then he suggests a special dessert.  A pastry with fruit which has an Indian name and he says is his favourite. He serves me a very big helping. Too much food. It is covered in a kind of custard.
koalas. Saving koalas. Being quite distressed about koalas.

A friend was filming a music videoclip in japan on a boat. Everything was 1950s decor, pastel pinks and lime greens.  There was a female dancer that was running around the boat. The boat turned into a restaurant/ spa. There were people in Onsens, and a giant kitchen making 5 star food. There were live cooking shows for entertainment and a tv show being filmed in the kitchen. It was so busy, so much going on. The restaurant had white lights shining down from the roof and they were making beautiful patterns on the floor. There was a big display case that looked like it had a miniature version of a beachside scene with mountains and clouds above but it was all made of different foods.

There was a huge fancy gala event at a rich castle . Everyones was dressed in gowns and black tie. Rihanna and Lizzo were dancing on rollerblades as if in a videoclip as part of the events live entertainment.  There was a dinner at this event that was to get investors for a new adult entertainment site that a suited man was organising. The table was full of the women that would be on the site, and it was advertising the whole thing as being female run, and safe for women/ empowering.   Then the dream fast forwarded a few years, and all the women were locked in hotel rooms or apartments all over town. The suited man who was speaking to the investors at the event held the key to all the rooms. The man setup cameras in all the rooms to monitor the girls, and put trackers on them so if they got away he could find them. The women realised they'd been trapped and this was not what they'd signed up for.

I was with 2 of my closest male friends, we were trying to get to a location that was an end goal in a life quest. I looked around and realised we were in the astral plane, there wasn't any ground we were hovering in air. Then it turned into a video game and we had to climb obstacles to get to an elevated platform. When we got there my friend cut his hand and it dripped blood, but the platform wasn't solid (was sort of invisible) and the blood passed through it and dripped down into the infinite astral plane we were floating through. The blood drops kept dripping forever.

I'm walking through a dimly lit subway in America, there's no one around.  I walk up some stairs to get onto ground level, as I'm walking up a man in coming down the stairs and looks at me. I feel scared and put my hands into my pockets and wrap them around my keys, ready to defend myself if I have to against this man. I wake up and I'm in my bed. I'm grasping a set of keys in each hand, holding on tight. Then I'm at a restaurant with Joe, and we're laughing about me waking up holding keys.  A woman who is a customer sits down at the table with us, and everyones clothes and the restaurant decor change from white to yellow. Theres a festival/wedding outside in a giant tent with a bar that goes for 1km long, there are hundreds of chairs setup in front of a giant music stage, to watch the wedding that will be held on stage.

I was at a high school farewell on a boat. It started sinking and I knew it was the new Titanic. I was the only person I could see on the boat, everyone else disappeared. I was rushing to pack a backpack with my clothes and my iPad which has all of my art work on it because I didn't want to loose all my art. I was trying to escape the rising water inside the boat to get outside and find a lifeboat where Beyonce will be doing a live performance, but I was too slow and kept dropping my iPad and having to pack it again.. and was watching the water rise. I see a room next to the one I'm in with all the other people, but it's to late for them they're stuck there. Water keeps rising and I'm not making a fast enough effort to get out. I'm too late.

I was in the city trying to get my UK visa from a news reporter who had taken it.  The water was rising in the city and everything was flooding so people had to stay on the top levels of buildings. There was a small op shop that was doing a fundraiser for it, my and 3 high school friends were all there accidentally wearing matching red outfits. I went to the bathroom in a cafe when we all went out for lunch and dropped my keys and phone into the toilet water. I then tried to walk out of the bathroom and almost tripped on a giant travel backpack lying on the ground that was mine and full of my clothes. I felt unsettled that all my belongings were in this open bag on the floor.

I slept with a friend of mine that I wanted to date, but he had a girlfriend and wasn't emotionally available and didn't want to date me. All his behaviour was extremely immature and emotionally unavailable and looking for someone to look after him.  I introduced him to my family but I accidentally called him by my ex's name. He had to go to a party, and I said I would give him a lift. Id seen a small business card with a breweries name on it on the floor and assumed that's where his party was, but the address we went to was actually a farm in outback Australia that was a red dusty paddock with one house in the middle of the paddock which was surrounded by green vines and a group of workers picking things from the plants to make whisky with. The house was white, the grass was vibrant green, but everything else around was red dust. The workers picking from the vines were dressed in long white dresses and wearing bonnets like in a cult, I knew it wasn't safe to be here and wanted to leave. I spotted a giant red dust hurricane in the rearview mirror coming towards us, and tried to start the car but it wouldn't start. We both started panicking and moving the gear stick and frantically pressing buttons, because we both couldn't start the car and the hurricane was now much closer. the hurricane was about to hit us.

I was at uni but it was in Germany not Australia. I sat next to a cute guy who looked similar to my ex, I knew this guy was a replacement/kinder version of my ex and that my ex would somehow see me happy with this new guy and that he would be jealous.   Me and uni guy went to a bottle shop that was also a camping store and one of the male staff members who was physically intimidating and large attacked me, he was acting mental and wild like a rabid dog. An old male friend from high school showed up and fought him off and I ran away.  I ended up at a Tony Robbins show and somehow snuck up on stage and out through a door in the back of the stage that was covered by sheer fabric, to the backstage area. The backstage area was an old Victorian era ball room, with sheer fabric on it's many doors and windows. There were an unusually large number of windows and doors and all their fabric was blowing in the breeze, but there was nothing outside it was just clouds and sky like the room was floating in air. My school friend and uni friend showed up in the room then, everyone was naked except for these black futuristic shoes with red flashing lights that let you hover above the ground, we started using them to skate around in the air like a roller rink.   We were then outside at night and went past a pub and there was a creepy old man leering at me outside, I remember wanting to get away from him and go inside because he made me feel preyed upon. I ended up running home from the pub alone.  Then it was day time and I was at the beach and kept loosing my thongs in the sand. It was slowing me down to keep looking for them, and a group of people who I was competing in a marathon with ran ahead and left me behind. A childhood friend showed up and helped me find them. Then we went into the surf lifesaving club at the beach and I started to do an auction online of all their clothing to make them money. Then the cops showed up and accused me of stealing which I hadn't. They asked to look inside my handbag, thinking they'd find clothes, but all there was, was a tiny golden moth that looked like it was made out of the cogs from inside a watch.

I went on a date to a guys house, covid was still around because he lived above a bar and the bar had restrictions on how many people were allowed into their courtyard. You could see the courtyard from the guys upstairs window and it was empty. He had an unusual broken guitar with two fretboards instead of the normal one , that was sitting upright on his couch. He was repairing it and learning to play and was bragging about it as if it would impress me. I didn't tell him that I was a talented guitarist and that I would be able to play that one. Then some of his friends showed up to his house for a dinner to meet me which was odd because this was the first time I was meeting the guy.  When the guy looked at me, he had the same eyes as my ex and I felt he was a representation of my ex in another form. I felt uneasy because I felt like I didn't know him well enough.  I went downstairs to the bar to get more beers to bring upstairs and a woman was giving birth in the courtyard of the pub. I spoke to her, but then became aware that I was speaking to her spirit because she was explaining the birth that was happening in real time as if it was a past event and therefor her real self and body was in the future. So there were multiple timelines and worlds existing simultaneously.

I was at a restaurant with a friend eating cake for dinner with a blue cherry ripe milkshake, then we went to a party. It was at some strange mans apartment. I wanted to leave and was going to drive home but someone reminded me that iso curfew time restrictions were in place and that I wasn't able to leave or I would get arrested. I felt trapped and uncomfortable, not safe. There were a bunch of people on drugs in the lounge room of the apartment and I didn't want to be near them, they were zoned out like zombies. A girlfriend of mine was also stuck there, she tried to sleep in one of the beds and I lay next to her and tried to comfort her because she was sad and curled up in a little ball.

Went to the movies with mum in a country town, with one main street. The movies were in an old 3 level ornately designed theatre. We went over the road to a supermarket to get snacks. I was aware that everyone was not wearing face masks and started to panic. I realised I wasn't wearing one either and was scared I would get covid. Someone told me the law had changed and that we didn't need to wear masks anymore.

It was my birthday, we were in an old run down house, that had walls decaying and paint flaking off the walls, the roof was caved in, in some rooms. There was a young man that god stuck under a decaying grand piano, he couldn't get out and I tried to help him so he wouldn't get crushed but no one would let me save him. One of my aunts in the dream told me not to worry and to cut the cake instead and do speeches. I was sarcastically agreeing with them "yeah your right cakes more important than a mans life" to see if they would realise they were being cruel but they didn't notice. Will Ferrell was my dad, and started trying to run my bday like it was an exercise class. Will Ferrell was wearing a colourful womens 80's lycra bodysuit. Then the house burnt down and we were on a boat and Cameron Diaz showed up as a zen master with japanese bonsai around her, and then her and I went on a date.

There was a serial killer on the loose, I was at a school that must have been my primary school, but I has my work computer there so must have been an adult. I turned into a detective and had to workout who the killer was. Everyone was locked inside the school, with the killer and I had to catch them before they killed again. One of the students was suspected of being the killer.  They started releasing people out of the school one by one, and I was let out, but forgot my bag with my work laptop and had to go back to get it. There were naked women dancing with colourful lightsaber/laser sticks blocking the door back in and as I tried to get past them they attacked me and burnt my skin with their lightsabers and I could feel it, and tried to push through the pain to get away from them.   Then I somehow got away and ended up on a beach out on a jetty that went 5 km out onto the ocean. I was watching a micro plankton swimming, it got eaten by a slightly larger creature, then another slightly larger one ate that one, and it kept going and going- more fish eating each other until it got to the size of a shark. It was the oceanic food chain in real time. As I was watching the shark eat another animal my vision zoomed out to a birds eye view of myself and I was a tiny dot standing on a jetty in the middle of the ocean and a huge stingray was under neither me under the jetty, it would have been 20m long. terrified.

I was in my backyard trying to grow plants and arrange them in pots to look nice. Mums abusive ex husband showed up at the house and I didn't feel safe. I wanted to kick him out but was too scared he would attack me so I hid in my old childhood bedroom, but it was different and all my belongings were gone, it was just an empty room. Then I was in a futuristic hospital/church about to give birth and I turned into Pam from the tv show the Office. These two loud and obnoxious women who were my friends in the dream burst into the hospital room with champagne and said they wanted to go on a holiday to Bali. They tried to jail break me from hospital to go on holiday. We got on a plane but never got off the plane we just stayed there forever. Mark Groves was on the plane, and interviewed one of the obnoxious women for his podcast, but he wasn't his lovely evolved and spiritual self that he is today, he was 20 years younger and had dyed his hair black and was a old player self. Mark and the obnoxious woman were flirting and everyone thought it was over the top and embarrassing.

I was at a school camp/festival. There was a man on the loose trying to hunt down one of my friends to kill her. I had to run through the festival grounds to find her to save her. When I found her she was in a big soccer stadium about to go on the field. She was wearing my AFL footy jumper, which was strange. She ran onto the field as the evil man got there, the crowd knew he was dangerous as I'd told them, so the crowd all gathered and made a human shield around the soccer field to protect her.

I was in a car with a friend on the way to a party and we were driving down a highway in the Australian outback. There was a river next to the road and my friend said she intuited a feeling of danger and needed to stop and get out of the car and walk down to the river to see. When she did she found a dead body in the water, it was a suspicious drowning. We had to run away we were scared someone would see us and come after us.

I was on a girls weekend away with a group of friends. We realised the airbnb we had booked had a second house attached to it with a group of guys were knew from our hometown. The guys were normally kind people but were all acting dangerously and scaring us. One of them had a knife and was trying to get through the joining wall in the houses to hurt us.  Another one of the guys came into our house to apologise for his friend but when we agreed that the friend was being scary, the guy changed his kind attitude and started saying it was likely our fault that his friend was trying to attack us. He left back to the guys house and all us girls knew we needed to escape.  There was a small air vent in the wall near the ceiling, which we all climbed through and replaced the grate so it wouldn't look different from the outside and the men wouldn't know where we'd gone. The vent lead into the Garden of Eden which was full of women (no men at all) and we knew this was our safe utopia. We all lived there safely and happily and one day a new woman arrived through the vent, I knew in my gut there was something off about her. She soon disappeared which meant the must have gone back through the vent to the real world.   When she came back she bought the men with her, having shown them our secret entrance to this world. She had been a spy for them all along. The Garden of Eden got dark as men poured through the grate, clouds covered the once blue sky. The men started hitting on the women and being creepy, trying to get their numbers or touch them.

I was on a farm with an ex boyfriend and his dad.  Me and the boyfriend were planning seeds in the soil which represented our future investment and relationship growth. His dad was standing over watching what we were doing, it felt rude to tell him he shouldn't be there so I didn't but his presence felt intrusive.  As we were planting the seeds, my ex got bored and walked off. I got angry and decided to quit as well and went to a bar with a friend for a drink.

We were at a mates house, and in her bedroom there was a bar.  A stripper friend of mine was bartending, everyone was suspicious that she was stealing from everyone while they weren't looking. I went on a walk with the parents of the girl who's house we were at. We took her 2 dogs, and were walking along a cliffside next to the ocean. We see drones flying above and my vision goes to a birds eye view. The drones are making video footage for the police because they know there's a killer on the lose around these cliffs. We go back to the house to get away from the killer. At the house, we notice one of our friends is missing and I realise they must have been the victim of the killer.  One of friends gets angry at me for drinking his orange juice, I truthfully tell him the bartender gave it to me and didn't tell me it was his which she knew. Then I realised she'd set me up.

I was walking through the city, covid restrictions in place and it was quiet. A mans dog barked at me and pulled at it's leash, the man told me it was safe to pat it but I knew it was not and that it would hurt me. I ran away, and am standing outside on the street on Swanston street and see 2 cops walk past. I'm pregnant and scared of the police, and scared of being a new mother soon. I think that I won't be a good parent and am anxious. The police peoples uniforms change from Australian cops uniforms to UK cops uniforms and I realise we're actually in a crime drama TV show.

I was in the car with my dad and he was driving. We were listening to the radio and a police report about a murderer on the loose came on. Suddenly I realised the murderer was my dad and that we were driving to a kindergarten so he could kill a child that told the police he was the man they should be looking for. I tried to stop him but he wouldn't listen to me, he got out of the car and I curled up in a ball and cried and hid from the world. I don't know if he killed anyone at the kindergarten as the police showed up, and may have gotten there in time.  I ran away and ended up at a work friends house with him and his wife and they were cooking me dinner. They took 5 hours to make dinner and I remember watching the clock and wanting to leave but not wanting to be rude. The wife kept telling me that I was doing things wrong (patting their dog wrong, folding a towel wrong), and I remember feeling like she was being really controlling. We were wearing matching PJs.

In my dream I realised that I'd forgotten to review my stats analysis chapter of my uni book for my exam, I was panicking about not learning it in time for the exam. I then had trouble logging into the online exam portal. My desk suddenly was messy and I couldn't focus and I got really mad. I started throwing things and yelling and then had to clean them up which wasted more time, and made me have less time to do my exam.  I heard a noise in the front yard and a killer was out there on the loose. My legs were bleeding and I was running down the street, I think I'd broken a window and climbed out the window to escape and cut myself. I run to the beach
I was in a bar with my ex boyfriend and some other friends.  He was ordering a cup of tea at the bar. having a meal, and going somewhere.

I was a lot younger and had been at a party. I had to make my way to a bus stop to catch a bus. I and several other party goers were walking along in a place i was unfamiliar with. I didn’t know where the bus stop was or what time the bus was leaving. I was supposed to be meeting someone to travel home with but didn’t know where they were.

I travelled across a wide river on a small motor boat powered by a very old woman.  I was worried she didn’t know where she was going but we arrived at the minibus pick up point ok. I think I was worried I had left my handbag somewhere but wasn’t sure. Everyone else had arrived in a group for the minibus, I was the only person to arrive alone.  I was still concerned about my handbag, I had a rucksack but wasn’t sure if the bag would be inside. When the minibus stopped I stayed on to look for my bag after everyone else had got off. I didn’t find anything, but when I opened the door to get off, the minibus was driving by itself so i couldn’t get off. It stopped at the end of a track in the middle of nowhere and when I got off it started raining heavily.  I was worried because I couldn’t find my phone - I had to phone an old school friend I hadn’t seen for 30 years. We had just arranged to meet for coffee and I had to tell her I wouldn’t be able to make it. The thought of everything in my bag and it being lost, wha was I going to do? I didn’t know how long the minibus had been driving or where I was. It was sandy and muddy and getting dark and I had a very heavy bag plus a sprained ankle.

I went out the back door of my house into the garden, it was not my real house but I knew it was where I lived. It seemed to be an amalgam of houses I have lived in in the past. Our rabbit, an old family pet from several years ago, was standing there, she was thin and I realised I had forgotten to feed her for several days. I felt guilty, and releived that she was alive, and went to get some vegetables for her to eat. First I found a branch to give her some shelter. When I went back outside I couldn’t find her.  looking round the garden trying to find her.

In a large garage type room. Being pursued by someone who is trying to capture us. He tied one to the wall and while he was going after someone else I untied him, I had to climb on the kitchen table to do so. Then i was lying on a bed and the attacker came over to me, he kissed me on the neck, i just lay there with my eyes shut. I didn’t know if he was angry with me for realeasing the other guy, or if he was going to keep kissing me.

I was in a room, perhaps a school room for younger kids with toys and boxes of stuff around. I had a box with lots of my shoes in, think I’d lost it and not sure where it was, looking around the room but the boxes I looked in were the wrong ones.
I was on a coach coming home. I had a suitcase. With people I knew. The first stop was Holloway Road. I got off there as I thought I would get home more quickly

I was moving a lot of stuff out of my flat to be thrown away. There was one of those stairwells that go round and round down lots of floors and you could see down the middle. I was throwing things down and some children were helping me collecting stuff at the bottom. Then I decided to pass pillows down the centre to the child on the next floor down. And she was able to reach it and then pass it down to the next child. I wanted her to be the child I passed to because she seemed to be their leader ? At least older perhaps and more responsible? Then I started passing down more stuff. One was a pile of brightly patterned ironed bedding. I yelled to make sure it made it down safely. Then I wondered why I was throwing it out if I was caring for it so much and maybe I didn’t want to throw it out anymore. I looked out my window into the front garden. My basement neighbours were clearing out lots of old furniture which was in the front garden. They were talking to my immediate neighbour belo2 me and his girlfriend. It here were a lot of dining type chairs and I looked to see if they were my old ones from 10 years ago amongst them. I saw a posh old couple wandering about the garden path vaguely looking at the stuff.
My downstairs neighbour called up to me that he wanted to speak to me. And then Steven Fry said “John Betjamin was ... “ then I realised I was dreaming

Looking out the back window of my flat over the garden, people in a lower flat had made a roof terrace. They waved at me and said I should too. I saw that I could go out onto the flat roof by my flat as well if I opened the window and went through that way. I opened the window. It came away. I sent Rory my nephew out to sit outside. I asked him to be careful in case he fell through the roof. I realised it was his room. There was a sleeping baby in a cradle. I thought I should probably close the window in case the baby got cold. That’s when I realised the window had come off its hinges. I reached out and grabbed it, then I saw that it had been attached to a big vertical beam. That had come adrift and was sinking. That part of the outside had become water and the beam had almost disappeared by now. I grabbed at it. I got the top of it and pulled. It broke in 2 pieces. The bottom half was disappearing. I managed to haul it in. There was a girl who asked for another towel. I gave her one of Rory’s used ones. Then thought better of it. I took it back and told her I would give her a clean on if she brought back the other used ones she still had. I felt pleased with myself for my cunning.

I was waiting to take a shower in a crowded moving thing. Like a train but too big. Big windows so people outside could see in. I was wearing lingerie including stockings and suspenders. The water kept changing colour from beautiful aqua blue to slimy looking green. I was waiting for it to be nice again. Then I realised it was someone controlling the colour by turning a valve. So I got him to fix it and had my shower. We were in a station and people were looking in. Commenting about me. It was hard to get clean with the lingerie on. And I didn’t get to wash my hair with shampoo. Then I saw I had big red welts all across my chest and boobs. Like hives. Like bites or an allergy. I remembered having one or two small ones on my arm the other day. I realised was an allergy. Then realised it was my be lovely sweaters that were doing it. I thought I would have to send them back. That was very sad as they are lovely. Then I was trailing my way home along the streets of Oxford? I think. I was having to push/pull a trolley thing and carry a huge bouquet of bedraggled flowers. I was dressed like I had been to a wedding. Mine maybe. I didn’t have my glasses and couldn’t see where I was going easily. I came across a street cafe in a square. I tried to get through the tables but got stuck and had to retrace my steps and go around. Someone suggested that as they could see I was stuck. Then I had to go through a long walkway which was lined with people. All dressed up. Wedding guests. But it was the only way I could go. They told me I couldn’t go that way, I saw the bride and groom had just exited at the other end. There was a big gate and someone was swinging it shut. I went down the path to the gate even though everyone said I couldn’t/shouldn’t. I got there as she was trying to lock the gate shut. I argued with her until sh3 gave me the padlock. Sh3 was very tall, slim, blonde, in a white cream suit. She went away. I went through and swung the gate shut. I then locked it with the padlock. She had given me the key and I felt a bit guilty because I had no one to give it back to. But I didn’t have time to waste. The weather was bad now. Slushy and wet underfoot and I still had to push this cart all the way home. The flowers were very bedraggled now and were wilting and falling off th3 bouquet.
Being back at work. In the canteen with Simon and some others. Having trouble selecting what to eat as they didn’t have anything I wanted. Sitting on wooden benches.
lava lamp blobs of monochrome lights

I was in a block type city environment, the streets were full of activity, cars driving around, people walking around, a lot were wearing coats and carrying umbrellas, as the ground was we from rain, but it wasnt currently raining.  I was heading somewhere and was walking along the street, and walked straight into a city park, where there were some teenagers with a boom box, they were loudly playing an instrumental version of "The Human League" , "Dont you want me".  I went over to talk to them, but they seemed vague and weird, apart from the one wearing the beanie hat, who was focussed on shuffling a deck of cards. He noticed me after a while, and said something strange about losing his tortoise in the fountain, at which point he pointed to a large ornamental fountain in the park.  Seeing the fountain, and hearing about the tortoise, I went over to the fountain, and bent over to look in the water.  Before I knew it, I heard footsteps and (presumably the youths)pushed me into the fountain, and I went underwater for a couple of seconds.  When I came back to the surface I was in a different place... I was still in water, but my surroundings had changed to a spa swimming pool in what I think must have been a nice hotel.  I left the pool, and walked around and found a corridor with doors on each side, and  landscape paintings on the walls, green plush carpets, and big Carver chairs, and there was a golden retriever dog wandering around, and this was quite a long corridor.  I tried a few doors, and found them locked, and I carried on trying a few more working my way down the corridor.

I was with someone wearing smart clothes and went through a full height turnstile in a mesh link fence, next to buildings and hangars, onto a block concrete outdoor area, lots of markings and lights in the concrete, and some small jet aircraft. The time of day was late evening dusk, so it was partial light.  I knew I was at an air courier company. We went over to a white and blue plane parked up on a stand, and went up the steps, and then pulled on orange cords to pull the steps up and close the door, and the other guy turned the door lever 90 degrees. We went into the cockpit (there was no door to get in, it was open access) and the other guy sat down in the left seat, and I took the right hand side seat, and we both strapped in and put headsets on.  The other guy was talking through what he was doing, and flicked a load of switches, and all the avionics lit up, and gauges and dials stabilised, and then there was a whining noise then engine roar.  The other guy taxied us out, and got us lined up with the runway, and stopped at the yellow solid hold markings. I recall all the taxi lighting on the way there, it was only a short taxi, as it's a small airfield. The edge lighting, centre line lighting, blue taxi lighting off the runway further up and the red end of runway lights, and the hold/centre line markings were all vivid and visible.  A bit more commentary from the other guy, and it was my turn to take over the aircraft. I had the yoke, and my feet on the pedals, and the other guy throttled up, and we started going faster and faster, and I pulled back and we took off and started climbing, and the other guy flicked the undercarriage and other switches  I could see houses and roads with cars with their lights on, and the far away grey silhouette of some hills, and I realised I was flying the plane, but it was a jet rather than a light aircraft, so something was off, so it was 100% a dream. Realising it was a dream, I got very excited that I had just performed a jet takeoff and was flying it. Within seconds, the dream very quickly got shakey and foggy and I woke up.

I was in an unfamiliar supermarket, and the signs over the isles and writing on what was left of the products was in Cyrillic script, so it was a literally a Russian supermarket. I couldn't find my way round the store, as the signs made no sense and I'd never been there before. There were a lot of empty shelves, and very little of what I needed available, and when there was stuff on shelves people were grabbing and getting in each others way. The store was also fairly busy, so the other people in there were a bit obstructive to my progress round the store... Lots of the people in the store had headscarfs and were weather worn, like the Syberian plains people The dream emotions were feeling frustrated and worried that I couldn't get supplies

It is fairly dark (night time), and it's really cold (but no frost or ice). The ground is grass, and there is a thin layer of thick mist over the ground, like in horror films, although I can't see the ground from where I am, some of the mist is coming over the top of the pit, so I just know what the ground above is like somehow. I'm inside a rectangular pit, cut into the ground. The pit has smooth soft clay sides, and is dug deep enough (probably 10ft/3mtrs cubed dimensionally) that reaching up, jumping, or trying anything wont get me out of it. Inside the pit is a very nasty place to be, its damp, and it's fairly dark, and it's cold, and I have snakes slivering around in the pit with me, and I can feel them slivering across my feet, and up my legs and body.... as well as the snakes there are cockroaches crawling all over me, on my face, my arms, my body, in my hair, everywhere. I have all these horrible things just crawling and slivering all over me, while I'm trapped in this pit that's riddled with them, with no means of escape, even though I'm trying to get out. On the ground above me, and the pit, there are people in monks habits, whose faces I can't make out, walking about near the perimeter of the pit. They are carrying flaming wicker torches, and I know they are the ones who put me in the pit. I'm terrified, and I feel trapped, helpless and hopeless.
